(9, 192, 'Damas, Ateye Steve', 'ateyedemas@gmail.com', '08103543526', '1 Efubade Street, Sabo, Ikorodu, Lagos', NULL, '30', 'male', NULL, NULL, 'Dear HR,\r\n\r\nWith this letter and the attached resume, I would like to express my sincere interest in the Marketing Executive position you have available. As an accomplished and successful sales professional with 3 years of experience, driving sales enhancement and achieving sustained revenue increases, I possess a wide range of knowledge and talents that will allow me to contribute toward the success of your company.\r\n\r\nMy expertise lies in successfully developing and implementing effective sales strategies, directing large-scale marketing campaigns, and managing personal, trusting client relationships to maximize company profits. Throughout my career, I have achieved distinction as a top sales performer,  receiving recognition from management. Additionally, my proficiency in various social media channels and outlets positions me to make a significant impact on your company’s exposure and bottom line.\r\n\r\nI believe that with my wealth of experience, I will contribute immensely to the success of Snapnet Nigeria Limited.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to speaking with you soon.\r\n\r\nThank you for your consideration\r\n\r\nKind Regards\r\n\r\nAteye Demas', NULL, '2019-12-31 20:49:10', '2019-12-31 20:55:25', 3, NULL, NULL),
