(30, 219, 'Peace', 'peacenuyoodoh@gmail.com', '08161580033', '312 road, C close, block 3,flat 15,Festac town, Lagos State.', NULL, '23', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/4V9mCrg2SEJtGa5ZugsuNMnSpHWbTBZeyzJ05Z0r.docx', '<p>Odoh Peace Ojonuyo<br />\r\n312 road, C close, Block 3,Flat 15,<br />\r\nFestac town, Lagos.<br />\r\n10th March, 2020.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\nThe Hiring Manager,<br />\r\nSnapnet,<br />\r\nLagos,<br />\r\nNigeria.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Letter of Application</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My name is odoh, Peace Ojonuyo, I humbly write to express my interest in the position of Business Intelligence Developer. Snapnet is known for delivery of excellence in all the services provided and outstanding value to market and clients, which were the major values that attracted me to Snapnet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a graduate of Biochemistry from University of Ilorin, with Second Class Upper Division. I became very enthusiastic about data analysis because of my love for calculation and statistics right from my undergraduate years, After doing a research on data analysis I decided to take up the challenge to become a data analyst.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nI learnt Microsoft excel during my service year, took a course on Microsoft Power BI on udemy in January 2020 and started Oracle Business Intelligence at ERP School Africa on the 1st of February 2020, I can boldly say that I have a good background in SQL and data visualization on power BI. Learning all these has not only increased my interest in data analytics&nbsp; but has also created a yearning to apply these skills in an environment which is the standard of excellence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wish to be given an opportunity to contribute my leadership, innovative thinking, problem solving, communication as well as skills in Microsoft Excel, Microsoft Power BI and Oracle BI which I&rsquo;ve acquired all through my undergraduate years and still developing till now , in achieving Snapnet&#39;s goals. There is no better place to develop a career path like Snapnet. I will deeply appreciate the opportunity and give every task assigned to me my best efforts.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sincerely,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Odoh, Peace Ojonuyo</p>', NULL, '2020-03-11 04:07:34', '2020-03-11 04:07:34', 7, 'profile_photo/ibKY65ITMawlWjRVdlgfO6LvpsnAg9hVfbp6OU2O.jpeg', NULL),
(31, 222, 'Victoria Nwaneri Ijeoma', 'ekovictoria4@gmail.com', '08100291532', '1 wahabi banire close off idimu road egbeda lagos', NULL, '30', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/QEJcFlv0SjxCJzp6CEz154NZ5qZ6TJxBLQBTPCuL.docx', '<p>Dear hiring manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When I saw your posting for recruitment online I was eager to forward my resume for your review. A fresh graduate with strong leadership and interpersonal abilities, as well as a proven track record of exceptional team work amd continually improve sales and customer service results, I am prepared to significantly contribute to your firm in this role.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Adept at finding needs and wants of customers and to explain how the company&rsquo;s products can meet their needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Special talent for assisting customers with products selection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Excellent organizational and follow-up skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;d like to meet with you to talk further about my qualifications and to learn more regarding your needs. I will call you after five days to see if an interview can be arranged. Should you require reaching me in the interim, please call or leave a text message.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your time and consideration, and I look forward to hearing from you soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,<br />\r\nNwaneri Victoria&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-03-17 09:58:01', '2020-03-17 09:58:01', 3, 'profile_photo/nepi9FDTx0qcqwZdxXKpx3BAvvpkXy9Hzao8yeca.jpeg', NULL),
