(35, 227, 'Adedayo Iyanda', 'adedayoiyanda@gmail.com', '08188236915', 'Ogba, Lagos', NULL, '32', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/EbCOnhrGdsN0O2zFKs77OvwSEZXH0XjHZ2D8ur26.pdf', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wish to apply for the post of a Data Scientist in your Organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a Business Intelligence Analytics Consultant with 7+ years&rsquo; experience in data analysis and 2+ years in Business Intelligence Analytics. I specialize in solving business problems using advanced analytics techniques and getting actionable insight from data to help organizations make better business decisions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have experience with Oracle, Microsoft and IBM solutions. I am also a certified Oracle Cloud Platform Enterprise Analytics Associate. I have had the opportunity to deploy Business Intelligence solutions at an enterprise level and for some medium size organizations as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of my core skills are critical thinking, data interpretation, data warehousing, data modeling, data visualization, creating reports and machine learning. I am familiar with the following analytics languages; DAX, SQL/PLSQL, Python for data science and Quora Language of Excel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will love the oppourtunity to meet with you personally to dicuss further about this job oppourtunity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adedayo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>08188236915</p>', 'iyandaadedayoayoadebusinessintelligenceanalystemail:adedayoiyanda@gmail_SPC_comaddress:ogba_SPC_lagosphoneno:08188236915professionalsummaryiamabusinessintelligenceanalyticsconsultantwith7+years’experienceindataanalysisand2+yearsinbusinessintelligenceanalytics_SPC_ispecializeinsolvingbusinessproblemsusingadvancedanalyticstechniquesandgettingactionableinsightfromdatatohelporganizationsmakebetterbusinessdecisions_SPC_someofmycoreskillsarecriticalthinking_SPC_datainterpretation_SPC_datawarehousing_SPC_datamodeling_SPC_datavisualization_SPC_creatingreportsandmachinelearning_SPC_iamalsoacertifiedoraclecloudp