(36, 228, 'Louis Oboh', 'lssmrtoboh@gmail.com', '08067052142', 'no 13 kola akinlade street Lagos', NULL, '30', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/1rcWc53vldBApIhyaBhZXKbMDwSczwTs5UJQYFfl.docx', '<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am submitting my resume and cover letter for consideration for the Cloud Architect job at Snapnet Nig Ltd. which you have posted on your site. I am interested in joining your team and organization as I noticed that my qualifications and experience match your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you will note in my enclosed resume, I have been working as a Cloud Architect for sometime now. In particular, I have spent most of my time on the development and implementation of new cloud management software programs, management and maintenance of cloud platforms, and providing advice and recommendations to clients and coworkers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, I possess exceptional critical thinking and problem-solving skills, great technological expertise, and the important ability to perform well independently or in a team setting. Moreover, I am comfortable working in fast-paced and deadline-driven business environments. I&#39;m Certified Cloud Architect with more experience on the Oracle Cloud Infrastructure platform. WIth experience on 3 government projects(NIMASA,JTB and Bank Of Industries)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you feel that my qualifications and experience are suitable, I can be available for an interview at short notice. Thank you for your time and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I look forward to hearing back from you soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Louis Oboh</p>', NULL, '2020-03-20 19:25:34', '2020-03-20 19:25:34', 6, 'profile_photo/3Wm0ecQvhPloeB0xV2TF0q716d0hXX1uc1xpycPb.jpeg', NULL),
