(39, 233, 'Babatunde Ogundare', 'teephillips79@gmail.com', '08038271150', 'Flat 51B Block 5 Fidelis Adeyemi Close Otedola Estate Magodo Lagos', NULL, '38', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/NtUIof7EZ4rqtYStB2Gsc5uSvXOpOI3c0aTa7ZZn.', '<p>I want to indicate my interest in the Sales Professional&nbsp;role in your company as advertised.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a well versed administrative and technical support professional with over a decade cognate experience in fast-paced executive level environments of banking and retail pharmaceutical industries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I started my career working with an Executive who rose through the rank and is now the Group Managing/CEO of United Bank for Africa Plc. I am well familiar with the demands for pro-activity and&nbsp;problem-solving in a performance-driven corporate space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At UBA. I initiated the idea of&nbsp;automatiing the handling of&nbsp;internal and external correspondences&nbsp;in the Executive&nbsp;Office to track movements of sensitive items and maintain high level responsiveness expected of a busy office. Working with IT and other stakeholder departments, this was successfully implemented and is still in use today.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Within my short period at HealthPlus Limited, I oversaw the deployment of Microsoft Office Planner(MS Planner) for effective tracking of tasks and deliverables within the Management Team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am excited to do a cross-over to a technical sales role and I believe I would add immense value for the following reasons:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>I have excelled for over a decade working in the fast-paced banking environment with a senior&nbsp;management level staff .&nbsp;I am therefore accustomed to prioritizing workloads, interfacing with multiple senior level individuals and teams including corporate representatives on official visits to the office in which I work.</li>\r\n	<li>I have had the privilege of effectively interfacing&nbsp;with high level contacts especially within the banking industry and the public sectors most of which will facilitate selling. I believe useful contacts within target industries will enable the company meet its goals of closing sales with such contacts.</li>\r\n	<li>I studied engineering and I am particularly excited at the opportunity to acquire in-depth IT knowledge in the company giving me the capacity to provide same to prospective clients thereby solving real problems for such organizations.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>I would be delighted to interview for this role.</p>', NULL, '2020-03-30 04:59:55', '2020-03-30 05:08:18', 3, 'profile_photo/kwWSF4vkpP3yl6LE479OztXKusJy17gioD6wU2j6.jpeg', NULL),
