(41, 238, 'Omorodion George Tyrone', 'tyronebliss023@gmail.com', '08138328309', 'Plot 5,Alhaji rasaq adekola street,owode elede,ikorodu road,Adekunle bus stop,Lagos.', NULL, '32', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/WxMRTfAoGQIb4YLTmd4EaiUZSG6wa5BHhJk6eWii.doc', '<p>Dear hiring officer,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is with Keen interest that I apply for the position of solution sales professionals. Attached to this cover letters is my curriculum vitae for your review.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Prior before now,I had a stint with a production company where I rose to the position of a supervisor through dint of professionalism,commitment,integrity and honesty .Currently,I work with an energy firm where I function as a business development assistant and assistant sales manager. My optimum is guaranteed if given the ample opportunity to team up with your thoroughbred professionals . I look forward to hear from you&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Omorodion George Tyrone.</p>', NULL, '2020-04-08 11:17:59', '2020-04-08 11:17:59', 3, 'profile_photo/6nlQYQR6ooS6uIG3x4NSvWAofCNrwt16qJIQe7O6.jpeg', 'profile_video/MmwhFvQGujE0oJVoKxLEYTQle8JanMgCkxDndHX7.doc'),
