(43, 241, 'Moshood Adekunjo', 'adekunjom@gmail.com', '09053656224', '5, Lemo Street, Oshodi, Lagos.', NULL, '24', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/7fb3f5e22a4d3115546524cead1eab37.PDF', '<p>Moshood A. Adekunjo</p>\r\n\r\n<p>14, Adegbenro Street, Iwaya, Yaba, Lagos, Lagos, Nigeria&nbsp;|&nbsp;+2348149445945&nbsp;|&nbsp;adekunjom@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>28/10/2020</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dear Hiring Manager,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am pleased to learn of the availability of a Data Scientist position in your company. I have checked through the company&rsquo;s profile and I am delighted to find your company as a place where I can offer my skills, learn and help the company reach its goals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a graduate of computer science, I have a good background in mathematics, programming, logic, data structures and algorithms, python, SQL. While on the skills side, I have acquired fundamental knowledge and practical applications of Data Science. My focus has been on data science specializations such as:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Data Analysis&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Data Engineering&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Machine Learning&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Deep Learning&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using the above listed skills, I have worked broadly on a number of data science projects. My journey in data science has been an interesting and a non-stop learning one.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In my current role as a Data Scientist in iQube Labs, I have been opportune to play a major role in a project that involved enhancing twitter experience of twitter users. This project has helped me improve my data visualization and&nbsp;behavioural analysis capabilities, it involved me applying time series prediction, sentiment analysis, data mining and some other data science subsets. I was responsible for using data visualization to help users make meaning of their twitter data. I also served as product manager for the product and through my management, I was able to bring the project to completion. Working in this capacity allowed me to hone my interpersonal communication skills and ability to present complex technical information to non technical personnel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have worked on&nbsp;other projects&nbsp;where I have been able to put into good use my analytics skills. Data science is a lifelong learning field and every project has help improve me greatly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing back from you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sincerely,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Moshood A. Adekunjo</strong></p>', 'moshooda_SPC_adekunjodatascientistiamaresourceful_SPC_self-motivated_SPC_resultandlearningdrivenprofessionalwithimpressivedataanalyticsanddatascienceability_SPC_iampassionateabouttechnologywithinterestsindatascience_SPC_researchandenhancinghumanexperience_SPC_ihaveexcellentinter-personal_SPC_communication_SPC_andtechnicalskills_SPC_adekunjom@gmail_SPC_com08068905329_SPC_090536562245lemostreet_SPC_oshodi_SPC_lagos_SPC_nigerialinkedin_SPC_com/in/moshood-adekunjogithub_SPC_com/ade-adelekeskillsdataanalysisbusinessintelligencedataengineeringmachinelearningdeeplearningwebdesigndevopstoolsandtechnologiespythonsqltableauibmwatsonstudiopysparkgooglecolabpowerbiawsflasklinuxgitexcelworkexperience10/2019–presentdatascientistiqubelabslagosanappliedcomputersciencer&dcompanythatprovidessolutiontoproblemsthatarelocallyrelevantusingstate-of-the-arttechnologies_SPC_clean_SPC_manipulateandanalyzelarge_SPC_complexdatasets_SPC_spanningawidevarietyofsources_SPC_identify_SPC_investigateandexplaintrendsandpatternsindata_SPC_provideinnovativesolutionstocustomizedmodeling/scoring/targetingwithappropriatemachinelearningmethodsoranalyticstools_SPC_workedwiththeteamtosupportallclientsmodelbuildingneeds_SPC_includingmaintainingandimprovingcurrentmodeling/scoringmethodologyandprocesses_SPC_workedwiththeteaminmovinganalyti