(44, 242, 'Raphael Agbojo', 'agbojoraphael@gmail.com', '08165799094', '16 Olukolu Street, Igbo Efon, Lekki, Lagos State.', NULL, '25', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/6mdNZhQELDiHKq5esWBhK23ZvdnqS9SyKayWAlqC.pdf', '<p>Hi,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Good day,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing to express my interest in the BI Developer role in your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have a proficient SQL skills in various RDBMSes such as Oracle, PostGreSQL, MS SQL, and also with NoSQL databases eg. MongoDB. I have vast experience in using data to build very descriptive dashboards beneficial to business growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have advanced knowledge in using reporting tools, such as, PowerBI, MetaBase, Redash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe in SQL optimisation, ensuring that queries run fast and results are spooled in a fast and efficient way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am confident I will bring to this position excellent skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for the consideration, and looking forward to hearing from you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regards,<br />\r\nRaphael Agbojo</p>', 'agbojosundayraphael16_SPC_oba-olukolu_SPC_igboefon_SPC_lekki_SPC_lagos_SPC_+234-816-579-9094agbojoraphael@gmail_SPC_compersonalstatementardentbelieverthatconstantinnovationandinventionintechnologyhasthepotentialtotakeafrica—andbyextension_SPC_theworld—fromwhereitistowhereitneedstogetto_SPC_careerobjectivetoworkinanorganizationthatwillenablemeharnessmyabilitiesandtocombinecreativeworkexperiencewithaproactiveself-growth_SPC_talentandresourcesthatwillcontributesustainablevaluetowardsthegrowthoftheorganizationandthenation_SPC_personaldatadateofbirth08-10-1995gendermalemaritalstatussinglestateoforiginogunstatenationalitynigerianreligionchristianityacademicqualificationswithyear2014-2018babcockuniversity_SPC_ilishan-remo_SPC_ogunstate_SPC_bsc(hons)degreeincomputerinformationsystems_SPC_‘firstclass’2006-2011epicinternationalschool_SPC_irewon_SPC_ijebu-ode_SPC_ogunstate_SPC_wassce(westafricanseniorschoolcertificateexamination)certificate2000-2005epicnurseryandp