(46, 247, 'Daniel Akinwumi', 'danielakinwumi@gmail.com', '08063197789', '17 iyalode close ogba ikeja', NULL, '27', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/N9f78XSurDfz1VmHNECToqrp5CkAHxxRYzoUSkw3.docx', NULL, NULL, '2020-04-25 10:21:15', '2020-04-25 10:21:15', 1, 'profile_photo/SsjzfJROog1TCgnA0Fi32CRw1F3EsN081L2GzbP4.jpeg', NULL),
(47, 248, 'Oshingbesan Adebayo', 'oshingbesanadebayo@gmail.com', '08109250377', '23, Adalemo Street, Off Ilogbo road, Ota.', NULL, '22', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/Y3hXutXAk6UBYVeqEjzUBVKA7jFKrK1k9y1zQSGG.pdf', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/ Madam,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LETTER OF APPLICATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Having reviewed the job description for the advertised role, I am submitting this cover letter alongside my resume for your review. Based on my experience in using data analytics, machine learning, and deep learning principles to build solutions, I am confident that I would be of significant benefit to your organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From data curation to results analysis, I am adept at assessing a project scope, determining the requirements, defining an objective, proposing an initial modeling hypothesis, and experimenting to build the best solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please see below a highlight of my professional and academic experience:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I earned a Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Engineering from the University of Ibadan in 2019. I also earned two other certifications in Business Analytics and Data Science from Wharton Online School of Business and Microsoft Professional Program respectively in the same year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I have developed several tools using data analytics, machine learning, and deep learning techniques. An example is a machine learning assisted log interpretation module. This module saved petroleum engineers a minimum of eighteen work hours on average</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I am currently ranked in the top 1% on Zindi Africa &ndash; a platform for competitive machine learning in Africa and finished 3rd in the nationwide machine learning hackathon 2019 organized by Data Science Nigeria</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I am competent in the use of the following tools &ndash; Python, SQL, R, C++, Microsoft Office Suite, and cloud resources such as Azure and Colab.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With my previous experience, other qualifications as highlighted in my resume and overall personality and character, I am confident that I will swiftly surpass your expectations for this role. I look forward to discussing the position in further detail. Thank you for your consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Adebayo Oshingbesan</p>', 'adebayooshingbesanhttps://www_SPC_linkedin_SPC_com/in/adebayo-oshingbesan•+2348109250377•oshingbesanadebayo@gmail_SPC_comapassionatelearnerwithastrongbackgroundinengineeringandprogrammingandin-depthknowledgeofmachinelearning_SPC_datascience_SPC_anddeeplearningtechniques_SPC_interestedinrolesthatwillfurthermycorecompetencies_SPC_-corecompetencies--dataanalytics-scientific/engineeringresearch-machine/deeplearning-cloudcomputing-programming(python_SPC_r_SPC_sql_SPC_c++)-written/oralcommunicationprofessionalexperiencemachinelearningengineer_SPC_cyphercrescentlimitedjune2019–presentbuiltmachinelearningsolutionsinproprietarysoftwareandcarriedoutnovelmachinelearningresearchinfieldssuchasnaturallanguageprocessing_SPC_computervision_SPC_amongothers_SPC_selectedkeycontribution:designedaknowledge-graphbasedarchitectureforanintelligentchatbotusingdeeplearningandnaturallanguageprocessingwithin60daysofinitialhiring_SPC_datascienceintern(remote)_SPC_onefinance&investmentlimitedfebruary2019–april2019skillfullyderivedvaluableinsightsfromcustomers’datausingmachinelearningtechniquessuchasboostedtrees_SPC_ensemblemodeling_SPC_timeseriesanalysisamongothers_SPC_selectedkeycontribution:automatedcustomersegmentationanalysisprocessthatyieldedatimesavingsof40%_SPC_dataanalyst(remote)_SPC_pilgrimstechnologyapril2018–january2019trackedkeyperformanceindicatorsandidentifiedgrowthopportunitiesleveragingmachinelearninganddatasciencepipelines_SPC_selectedkeycontr