(48, 250, 'Godwin Oguche', 'godwinjunior@hotmail.com', '08037708813', 'No. 6, Sule Abore street, Ojodu, Lagos State.', NULL, '33', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/m4lEIJIWR6iiaxj5vOKMjJC1he7iUl6SorOrlxVz.pdf', '<p>To whom it may concern,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindly accept this application from a highly enthusiastic, motivated, and knowledgeable professional who wishes to apply as a Data Scientist in your highly esteemed organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am currently engaged as a Service and Quality Management Analyst in the Service Quality and Innovation Department in the Banking sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am proficient in Statistical analytics tools as I employ them to carry out my every day duties at the bank. I am particularly suited to Power BI and proficient in both Python and R programming languages. I am also proficient in Microsoft Office packages of which MS Excel and Power BI are among my strong suits. I have a strong presentation and analytical skills which I bring to bear in any organization I am associated with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a graduate of Computer science from the Federal University of Technology, Yola in Adamawa State; now renamed as Modibbo Adama University of Technology, Yola. Additionally, I am able to identify and strategically exploit any campaign for maximal impact through the use of data. With my current employer &ndash; Unity Bank, I constantly exceed all performance targets set for me, and I am valued for my ability to deal with complex situations by coming up with unique and fresh perspectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have an experience of over five (5) years in this sector and I am very keen to join your company because you are able to offer employees an array of impeccable career and growth opportunities. I possess excellent management skills including client relationships, negotiating, dispute resolutions and critical thinking. I would be grateful for the opportunity to showcase my abilities further at a personal interview. Please feel free to communic