(55, 279, 'Adeyinka Michael', 'adeyinkakayolass@yahoo.com', '07031875874', '1 Oba Saheed Elegushi Road, Jakande Estate Lekki-Epe Expressway Lagos', NULL, '39', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/WIh1VKMFnY27CN5xKeejCUo40HEKphCY10AS9Dg8.doc', '<p>&nbsp;The Human Resources Manager,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Snapnet&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;Lagos.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; APPLICATION FOR A POSITION IN YOUR ORGANIZATION<br />\r\nIn reference to the advertised position, I wish to declare my interest for the positionn of a Sales/Marketing Professional in your reputable establishment. Kindly find my CV attached. As highlighted in my CV, I havee seven years of successful professional experience and track record that clearly demonstrates my skills and qualifications to contribute in a major role in your organization. A review of my credentials will quickly confirm that I am a skilled and hard-working professional with a propensity for continuous improvement.<br />\r\nI am a Professional with hands on experience in providing specialized services in Client, Services, Customer Care, Channel distribution, Key account management, Territory/Area Sales Manager,Media/Public Relations, Business Development, Customer Relations, Logistics/Protocol, Sales and Marketing, Brand and Marketing Communication.<br />\r\nI possess a Bachelor of Science in Mass Communication from Lagos State University, Lagos and I have professional certificate from Nigeria Institute of Public Relation and Chartered Institute of Marketing United Kingdom in view just to mention a few.<br />\r\nThroughout my career, I have strives to keep business objectives in the forefront, be it in a secondary or leadership position. Focusing on business to business and clients to business imperatives is a core value of mine, one that I bring to every assignment on which I work. Hhaving attained