(73, 295, 'David Davies', 'daviesodavid@gmail.com', '07064680904', 'No 1 Durosinmi, Abayomi Etti Street, Marwa, Lekki, Lagos', NULL, '25', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/lFsRPHuoOPsUwBs74tckWQ7ySrOEq9CoyfH7xphj.pdf', '<p>I am excited to be applying for this job position. As someone with a lifetime experience with mathematics and strong quantitative reasoning, I thrive in digging into complex data sets and producing insightful, data-driven strategic recommendations. With this, I&rsquo;m very much eager to turn my talent for analyzing big data into actionable growth strategies for the organization.<br />\r\nI have experience working as a data analyst in the telecom sector supporting sales, marketing and executive teams with recurring insights and ad hoc data analysis. From my work on Revenue Assurance and Fraud Management projects, I have had the opportunity to sharpen my skills in data analytics from data collation, analysis, reporting and presentation. I have also been able to master techniques that has enabled me develop strong analytical strategies to optimize business processes and locate improvement opportunities. Within these capacities, I have had the opportunity to be of immense benefit to firms like Ntel Nigeria, MobiusWS and Dangote.&nbsp;<br />\r\nI am fluent in a variety of software and data management systems ranging from Excel, Power BI,&nbsp;Microsoft SQL Server. I have knowledge in front end development (html, CSS and JavaScript) and currently advancing well in Machine Learning&nbsp;with&nbsp;Python for advanced data analytics strategies.<br />\r\nI&rsquo;m looking forward to learning more details about this position. I believe my experience in statistical approach and problem solving in data analytics makes me of great benefit to the business community and the organization in particular.</p>', 'educationexperience+2347064680904lekki_SPC_lagosdaviesodavid@gmail_SPC_comdaviesdavid2019nationalyouthcorpsservice2018associationofcharteredcertifiedaccountants