(74, 318, 'Alalade Toluwani Felix', 'toluwani1991@gmail.com', '09026482015', '26, jadesola oshodi street, off Brown road, Aguda, Surulere, Lagos', NULL, '28', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/oeY0neyypoWvfbY2JNK0y00abJgHxRyrZOEQ9mbW.docx', '<p>I am writing in response to the opening for the position of a Data Scientist in your reputable organization. I believe it is a great match for my skills and experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through work and study, I have acquired the competencies and skill-set to succeed in this role. I hold a Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Pure and Applied Mathematics from Bowen University, Iwo. My background includes Algebra, Mathematical Methods, Mechanics, Dynamics, Mathematical Physics, Programming and currently Data Analytics and Reporting. Through my previous and current role as a Marketing Analyst, Value Management Analyst, Data Engineer, Data Architect, Insights and Analytics team member as well as Head, Data Engineering and Analytics, I have gained valuable experience in data engineering, data architecture, performance monitoring, business intelligence, business analysis, reporting, dashboard building, financial modelling, geo-analytics, machine learning and data analytics as well as leveraging on big data to achieve predictive analytics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an excellent Mathematician with rear analytic skills, I hope to leverage these skills and experience at your reputable organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a team player with top-notch communication, analytical and organizational skills. I am proficient with MS Word and Excel, Microsoft Dynamics, Microsoft Azure, Oracle Business Intelligence, SQL(MySQL,Oracle SQL,SAP HANA SQL, TSQL,PL/SQL), M-Code, DAX, R and Python with a deep understanding of python data libraries such as NUMPY for scientific computations, SCIPY for statistics, optimizations, integration and linear algebra packages used for computation, SCIKIT-LEARN for data analysis and mining, PANDAS for data structuring and analysis, STATSMODELS for data exploration, statistical analysis and assertion and MATPLOTLIB for visualization in charts and graphs format &nbsp;as well as R data libraries such as DPLYR for data manipulation, CARET for classification and regression model training, GGPLOT2 for data visualization, SHINY for building interactive web apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have built predictive models, classification models such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Churn Prediction Model</li>\r\n	<li>Predicting Financial Implication of Network Downtimes</li>\r\n	<li>Customer Segmentation Model</li>\r\n	<li>Next Best Offer/Action</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For a leading financial institution and also a leading e-commerce company in Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have also built Data Warehouses using ETL tools such as PENTAHO, SSIS. I have built an end to end reporting and analytics framework for both companies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would welcome an opportunity to discuss my qualifications and candidacy in further details. I am available for an immediate interview and can be reached on <strong>09026482015</strong> or via email at <strong>toluwani1991@gmail.com</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks, in anticipation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best regards,</p>', NULL, '2020-04-30 14:35:12', '2020-04-30 14:35:12', 5, 'profile_photo/TdMUgJ1PBE8L5ghxbhW0iNZNWiCq4vokAVqhu6uv.png', NULL),
(75, 271, 'Williams Abodunrin Osei', 'williamsabodunrin@gmail.com', '08168971699', '36, Nuru Oniwo Street Aguda Surulere Lagos', NULL, '24', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/2iMOZhCp2rsoPy9Vi8pc4sOeWh5QZg3XBU63k3R8.pdf', '<p>Dear HR Manager<br />\r\nSnapnet,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am submitting my resume for consideration for the role of data analyst/scientist in your Company. Given the skills&nbsp; outlined in my enclosed resume, a fervent desire to learn and the testimonies of people around me,&nbsp; I&nbsp; believe I will be a worthy asset to your team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In my five&nbsp; years at Federal University of Technology Akure, I&rsquo;ve completed a great deal of coursework that I believe has given me some of the prerequisite knowledge I need to thrive in a financial organisation although I studied Engineering. These coursework includes Engineering Statistics, engineerig mathematics and advanced engineering&nbsp; mathematics where I learned and applied skills such as regressional analysis, anova, mathematical modelling Etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, I spent the last year(service year) in learning and building a career in data science. I took courses online some of which are stated in my resume and focused on the Python Programming language as a tool for data analysis/science. Ever since then I have tried to apply the things I learnt by working on personal projects where i performed data exploration on data downloaded online and used a machine learning algorithm to build predictive models</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, my few months&nbsp; as a kaggler in www.Kaggle.com, has opened my eyes to the beauty in technology especially data science( Kaggle is an online community for data scientist). I have entered into competitions and built models that are evaluated, scored and ranked together with other competitors. This has expanded my mind as I had the opportunity to go through other competitors models and learning from them. In the process of reviewing models from higherly intellectually people, my skills have developed in turn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe I would make an excellent addition to your team. This job would help me grow my real-world experience in the technology industry and help me further develop and refine my analytical and computational skills..<br />\r\nI look forward to hearing from you!<br />\r\nSincerely,<br />\r\nWilliams Abodunrin Osei</p>', 'abodunrinoseiwilliams+234(0)8168971699williamsabodunrin@gmail_SPC_comcareerobjectiveyearningforanenvironmentwheremyskillsandknowledgecanbepracticedandusedtherebyincreasingmyprowessandinturnbecomingmorevaluabletothatenvironmentandtotheworldatlarge_SPC_iwanttogainexperienceandunderstandingbypractice_SPC_tobeabletoprovidesolutionstoorganizationalproblems(especiallyintheengineeringsector)atanyleveliamintheorganization_SPC_profilesex:maledateofbirth:20thdecember_SPC_1995maritalstatus:singlestateoforigin:ondostatelocalgovernment:irelelgaeducationalbackgroundeducationalinstitutionsattended(withdates)i_SPC_federaluniversityoftechnologyakure_SPC_ondostate(b_SPC_eng_SPC_)2018ii_SPC_nigeriannavysecondaryschoolibara_SPC_abeokuta_SPC_ogunstate(wassce)2012iii_SPC_princetonschools_SPC_surulere_SPC_lagosstate2006academicandprofessionalqualification(withdates)i_SPC_bachelorofengineering(miningengineering)–secondclass(honors)upperdivisionfederaluniversityoftechnology_SPC_akure_SPC_ondostate2018ii_SPC_3ddesignautocad_SPC_www_SPC_thesourcecad_SPC_com2018iii_SPC_pandas_SPC_geospatialanalysis_SPC_introductiontomachinelearning(certificateofcompletion)_SPC_www_SPC_kaggle_SPC_com2019iv_SPC_featureengineeringcertificateofcompletion:(addingmorefeaturestoadataset_SPC_modifyingexistingonce)_SPC_www_SPC_kaggle_SPC_comv_SPC_datavisualizationusingpythonprogramminglanguage(certificateofcompletion)_SPC_www_SPC_kaggle_SPC_comvi_SPC_intermediatemachinelearningcourse(certificateofcompletion)vii_SPC_advancedstatisticalanalysisusingpython(certificateofcompletion)viii_SPC_tableau(certificateofcompletion)ix_SPC_python_SPC_sql_S