(84, 324, 'Afolabi Onagbola', 'afoonagbola@gmail.com', '08143276899', '19, Prince Bode Adebowale Crescent, Lekki Phase 1, Lagos', NULL, '22', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/7k6ePxOErJXztehENTq9oMMmn3LI6EXRJVSxVm01.pdf', '<p>The Recruiting Team,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet Nigeria Limited</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Recruiting Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing to express my desire to join the Snapnet office in Lagos as a Data Scientist. I am&nbsp;confident that my previous experiences have prepared me&nbsp;well for the role. I have had quality&nbsp;experience in eTranzact, Nigeria&rsquo;s premier payment processing company, where I developed&nbsp;policies to guide the&nbsp;formation of an Internal Control department, of which I became a founding&nbsp;member. To do this, I gathered data to understand critical internal operations by&nbsp;asking the right&nbsp;questions, proposed a structured strategy to the Group Head and carried on to implement the&nbsp;agreed-upon changes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Soon after, I chose to examine the company&rsquo;s fraud losses and leveraged machine learning to&nbsp;understand subtle fraud patterns. Conducting fraud&nbsp;investigations that also required frequent use&nbsp;of statistical techniques has improved my analytical acumen. At eTranzact, I demonstrated&nbsp;initiative and leadership by developing a robust revenue assurance process and updating the&nbsp;settlement dispute process. While working on this project, I conducted interviews with all&nbsp;departments involved. This helped develop my interpersonal and diplomacy skills, as I had to&nbsp;liaise with department heads and staff to collect information and get them on board the new&nbsp;procedure. Solving organizational problems across diverse fields, like Operations Control and&nbsp;Systems Audits, has been most exciting for me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In taking on this role, I can leverage my strong analytical skills and a keen sense of initiative with&nbsp;strong project management capability. I would bring 