(90, 330, 'AbdulRasheed Lawal', 'Lawalabdulrasheedbolaji@gmail.com', '08133367208', '8 Dele Adeyemi Street, Lekki II, Lagos State, Nigeria', NULL, '23', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/LqdqgiIeZw3pRsrDVng3AI9h75hGSblPgBQet0qa.pdf', '<p>25th May 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lagos State, Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was pleased to learn about the available Data Scientist position at Snapnet. Having worked as a business analyst and freelanced as a data science and machine learning researcher on the world&rsquo;s largest platforms, including Kaggle and Hackerrank for the last 3 years, I am excited at this opportunity to translate my versatile suite of competencies into business success for Snapnet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My focus, as an emerging professional, is to utilize my strengths and technical capabilities to make a positive impact on the overall organization. In my current role as a Business analyst at Ariosh, I&rsquo;ve had the unique opportunity to lead pricing analysis by capitalizing on data mining, analysis and visualization techniques to offer competitive pricing recommendations to management on project bids. During this period, we achieved a 100% success rate on commercial bids.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an AI researcher with Carnegie melon university (through the AI Saturday Lagos Initiative), I&rsquo;ve had the unique opportunity to work extensively with machine learning models and utilize data science technologies including SQL and python, to infer marketing insights from unstructured data. Among my peers, I am regarded as an analytical whiz with expert problem-solving skills. I have a 5-star problem-solving rating on Hackerrank for medium to hard problem sets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I excel in a workplace that demands high-energy teamwork and does not compromise on growth. I strongly believe that my versatile skills set and business intelligence, make me distinctively valuable to Snapnet&rsquo;s growth as a provider of business Intelligence solutions in Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kindly find enclosed in this application, my resume, which provides further insight into my skill sets, accomplishments, and experience as a data scientist as I look forward to an opportunity to demonstrate my capacity to spur growth in your organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your time and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours truly,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abdulrasheed Lawal</p>', NULL, '2020-05-26 01:29:53', '2020-05-26 01:29:53', 5, 'profile_photo/vZAeGXPbAanr87e3GnVX4ABoQp6yZlFK37JrUVzq.jpeg', 'profile_video/CGuAMvVcoqp4ovnbOqG7oCpVEA2G7KdJFBzdEjBs.qt');
