(91, 325, 'BASIL IHUOMA', 'ihuomacbasil@gmail.com', '08104162457', 'Daniel Asomugha Close, Lake View Estate, Amuwo Odofin, Lagos State.', NULL, '27', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/ARYiY1lMaOeSfw4kAklnA2nDb01BgRg0crmXaPfb.pdf', '<p><strong>Basil C. Ihuoma&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Daniel Asomugha Close, Lake View Estate,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amuwo Odofin, Lagos State,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>May 20th, 2020.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Snapnet</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1b Abayomi Shonuga Crescent,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lekki Phase 1,</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lagos, Nigeria.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Recruitment Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sequel to the job post for the search of a Data Scientist at Snapnet on your website.&nbsp; I, Basil C Ihuoma, write to formally express my interest in the position with the conviction that I would be a valuable addition to your team.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I currently work with a luxury lifestyle brand in Lagos called Alara Multiconcepts Limited, as the Data Analyst for the retail business unit, a position I have handled for about two (2) years. My responsibilities include but not limited to; collecting and analyzing daily sales data, creating reports on business performance, providing insight on customer spend, and behavior based on data analyzed. Under this role, I have developed a compelling predictive analytics model which has helped the business in better merchandising and targeted marketing campaigns, and improved personalized product recommendation to customers based on their buying history using a recommendation model.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personally, I have carried out several projects which include:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a.) A credit-score card Classification Algorithm which helps banks determine if a loanee should be granted a loan or not.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b.) An accurate used car price prediction model that can assign a price for a vehicle by evaluating its features, taking prices of other cars into consideration. <em>&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://github.com/Sillians\"><em>Click Here</em></a> to view my portfolio.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My curiosity and passion for this field has helped me in gaining valuable skills in data science, machine learning, business, and cloud computing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am very keen to discuss further the goals of this role and show you how my skills and experience can translate into significant growth of Snapnet&rsquo;s bottom line.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many thanks for your kind consideration and I look forward to hearing back from you soonest.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your Faithfully;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/jnSRio5_oIo1K2LKb373mRjgNdgLipY6OoY7hLP3yA7F8F2yFDN9f8pbBrgKYNVCC_UQcjzPNJeD7t2LjlXtNEjcmJVOtcPqZ4lImvWGbReFKLUsuoL4zPFkZ7jBY8qvk6cQUd3pWW_m_qhTjQ\" style=\"height:37px; width:186px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Basil C Ihuoma</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'basilc_SPC_ihuomadatascientist||associatecloudengineer(gcp)​​gmail​​linkedin​​​twitter​​​github​mediumphone:+2348104162457address:danielasomughaclose_SPC_lakeviewestateamuwoodofin_SPC_lagosstate​_SPC_summarybasilisabusiness-orienteddatascientistwithaprovenrecordofprovidingtailoreddataprocessingandbusinessintelligencesolutionstodelivervaluableinsightstokeybusinessproblems_SPC_combiningsavvinesswithmoderntechnologiesinstatistics_SPC_datascience_SPC_andmachinelearningwithsoundbusinessacumenideliveractionablesolutionstoreal-worldbusinessproblems_SPC_iseekanopportunitytousemyskillsandknow-howinaresult-drivenorganizationthatencouragescreativity_SPC_hardwork_SPC_andself-development_SPC_keyskills●proficientinstructuredandunstructureddatacollectionandprocessing_SPC_●adeptapplicationofstatisticsandprobabilitytechniquesindatamodeling_SPC_●experiencebuildingsupervisedandunsupervisedmachine-learningmodels_SPC_●excellenttimemanagementskills_SPC_●greatabilitytoprioritize_SPC_