(105, 379, 'Emmanuel Azukaego', 'emmazuka@gmail.com', '08162668255', '5, Overcomers close, Oworoshoki Lagos', NULL, '29', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/L0OrdrV9pBLMsrL2yNoslJW0yLbV2cGPpsH4fqMg.docx', '<p>8th July, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Human Resource Manager,<br />\r\nSnapnet Technologies,<br />\r\nLekki, Lagos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Ma,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please accept my application for the Sales Executive position on your company&#39;s website. After reading the job description, I am confident that I would be a perfect fit for this role, as my experience and abilities precisely match your requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a sales-oriented professional with a sound client relationship management, customer satisfaction and retention, and people management. I possess astute business knowledge, and I have experience contributing to strategic planning while delivering improvements in processes, productivity, and costs. As a sales executive with Desprudave Technologies, I am currently part of a sales team of 4 members which maintain profit objectives, and analyze future trends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this my position, I foster strong relationships with customers and strategic associates. Having worked for 3years in this position, Imost&nbsp; times exceed targets given me. I simultaneously gained respect from staff and management through effective communication and liaison.&nbsp;<br />\r\nMy references will be happy to discuss my positive attitude and strong work ethic.<br />\r\nThank you for your time. I look forward to discussing my application further in an interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Emmanuel Azukaego</p>', NULL, '2020-07-09 22:27:06', '2020-07-09 22:27:06', 3, 'profile_photo/FUUcMCGOukVEe4U8KMv808jvBagC3obgIwuv5iKI.jpeg', 'profile_video/Lrf14aFrXsbZpoWrp1Zmg3BlCABNO5OsgTILo1WF.mp4'),
(106, 385, 'Ademola Adedapo', 'gigclaude@gmail.com', '07030207600', 'Akinremi Street, Anifowoshe, Ikeja', NULL, '29', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/QT7HwSEHYrHcXZ6bAlCJqGddzpRO1dSdWe8YzWqQ.pdf', '<p>An intense desire to make a difference&mdash;wherever I happen to be&mdash;has inspired my contributions in diverse sales and marketing roles over the years.One of the benchmark of my career in my present position include but not limited to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Increasing daily sales goal by cross-selling and promoting additional products and services; improved sales by over 25% in the last quarter of 2019, generating N1.5 million in a single transaction.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ability to connect with my employers and business vision, understanding their needs, and communicate the bottom-line benefits of developmental initiatives. I possess proven ability to deliver on results that are reflective of my level of expertise. I have served in five different roles with the primary purpose of sustaining rewarding partnerships and coordinating strategies that make companies thrive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I collaborate with multiple teams to implement and monitor projects as directed by management and see the projects through to completion. I steer efforts and strategies on development and technical functions while building upon existing efforts on daily tasks and projects utilizing expert skills, progressive experience, and technological tools to turn plans to realities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Much of my success in accomplishing business goals were attributable to the contributions I made as a versatile sales professional through due diligence, strategies implementation, and technical expertise. I am aware your organization needs an energetic sales soution professional to deliver across diverse verticals that will reflect organizational core values, it&rsquo;s a role I can perform actively based on my track record working with different teams since 2013<br />\r\nMy career has been personally rewarding because each challenge and successes become my own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I want every person within my sphere of influence to achieve success, and my highest aim is to make that possible. I am confident that my background and achievements would allow me to make an immediate impact in the advertised position. You may reach me through the contact information as the application process progresses</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks for your time and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,<br />\r\nAdemola Adedapo</p>', 'ademolaadedapoakinremistreet_SPC_ikeja_SPC_lagos_SPC_|+2347030207600|olukayodeadedapo@gmail_SPC_comsales&marketingaccountmanagementcustomeracquisitionsolution-sellingbusinessrainmakerwithbig-picturevisionandproactivesolutionsexperiencedmarketerfocusedonachievingexceptionalresultsintheareaofsales_SPC_marketing_SPC_customerservice_SPC_andaccountmanagement_SPC_playedasignificantroleinthenegotiationandexecutionofan10_SPC_5mdealwithinthefirstfewmonthsofemployment_SPC_top-performersupportingbusinessvisionwithinitiativesthatelevateperformance_SPC_profitability_SPC_growth_SPC_andcustomerretention_SPC_strategicarchitectinthedevelopmentandimplementationofinsight-drivenstrategiesthatexceedexpectations_SPC_effectiveinidentifyingopportunities_SPC_buildingrewardingrelationships_SPC_andincreasingsales_SPC_utilizingallchannelsofcommunicationtodevelopteammomentum_SPC_enthusiasm_SPC_andownership_SPC_careerbenchmarksledthemarketingdevelopmentteamonstrategiesalignmenttosupportmarketexpansionefforts_SPC_aidedtherolloutofmarketinginitiativesthatelevatedbusinessperformance_SPC_managed_SPC_eased_SPC_andwidenedproductdeliveryterritory_SPC_herebyincreasingcustomersby60%_SPC_amountington6_SPC_5minmonthlysalesonaverage_SPC_manageda5-membermarketingandproductteamactivelyinvolvedindrivingstrategicalignmentinsalesacrosslagosandtheentiresouthwesternstates_SPC_corecompetenciessales&marketingcustomerservicedigital&socialmarketingcustomerneedanalysisdrivingproblemescalationanalyticseff