ontribution to your company&rsquo;s operations, and able to&nbsp;<br />\r\nmanage multiple priorities at the same time. This would provide me with the ideal opportunity to assist your organization and to expand my skills.&nbsp;<br />\r\nKindly refer to the accompanying CV for more detailed information regarding my abilities and skill sets. If this brief account of my competencies intrigues you enough to invite me for an interview, please contact me at your earliest convenience. I appreciate your time and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\nYours faithfully,&nbsp;<br />\r\nOlabisi Akinbobola.&nbsp;</p>', 'personalstatementakinbobolaolabisicurriculumvitaepersonal+2348077955654olaniyiolabisi36@gmail_SPC_commotivatedeconomicsgraduateskilledinworkingcloselywithmentors_SPC_competentintheuseofofficeequipmentandsoftware_SPC_eagertolearnandtakethenextstepinthefinancialsectoroftheeconomywhilstprovidingsupporttoawell-establishedcompany_SPC_facilitator(nysc)bafotflourishacademy_SPC_agbado_SPC_ogunstateoct2018-oct2019facilitatedmathematicsandeconomicsattheseniorlevel_SPC_salesinterncrmbookshop_SPC_ogunstatejune-august2017marketingofchristianbooks_SPC_biblesandkeepingrecordsoffinancialtransactions_SPC_financeinternalconniglimited_SPC_riversstatejune-august2016archivedfinancialdocumentsinphysicalformsshadowedfinancialanalystsinthepreparationoffinancialdocumentsroadahousesd4b_SPC_obaadeyinkaoyekanestate_SPC_1hakeemdicksonroad_SPC_lekkiphase1_SPC_lagos_SPC_nigeria30september_SPC_1997socialeducationolabisi-akinbobolaworkexperiencecovenantuniversity_SPC_ota_SPC_ogunstateb_SPC_sc_SPC_economicsdegree:secondclass(lowerdivision)2014-2018king’scollege_SPC_lagosstatewaec:7distinctionsand2credits_SPC_mathematicsb2_SPC_englishc52011-2013professionalmembershipsstudentmember–associationofcertifiedcharteredaccountants(acca)studentmember–nigerianeconomicstudentassociation(nesa)_SPC_covenantuniversitychapter_SPC_dr_SPC_oluwatoyinmattheweconomicsanddevelopmentstudiesdept_SPC_covenant