(120, 456, 'Davies Jeremiah', 'daviesjray@gmail.com', '08184751962', '1 Abayomi wofeha Street, Destiny Homes Estate, Abijo, Lagos', NULL, '28', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/VPexhi28ghAoSOYRYfeg0XmLOfLDMwdigeg0lMyy.pdf', '<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the business world, having a strong, clear relationship with your clients is critical to overall success. Throughout my career, I have achieved career success by contributing to and impacting business outcomes through effective communication, sales pitching, organization, prioritization, and account management. I believe my skills and qualifications are an ideal match for the Solution Sales Executive role within your organization and will bring immediate value.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In my current role as a Business Development &amp; Sales Executive, I have exercised a calculated and methodical approach to problem-solving. I am independently motivated, yet I appreciate team efforts and collaborate productively within groups. Additionally, I am knowledgeable in lead generation and sales with proficiency in product demonstration. Furthermore, I am great at analyzing current situations and strategizing to bring about better results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This opportunity is especially exciting. I believe my communication and already established network within various sectors can aid lead generation; my problem-solving and customer service abilities will support and drive your continued organizational success. Furthermore, my analytical and problem solving skills have been made a core part of me&nbsp;due to my&nbsp;engineering background having studied and obtained a chemical engineering degree from Covenant University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To demonstrate the scope of my career history and professional competencies, please take a moment to review my attached resume. I appreciate your evaluation of my credentials and subsequent response.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jeremiah E. Davies</p>', 'eneonyej_SPC_daviesdedicatedsalesp