(133, 501, 'Abdulquadri Abdulazeez', 'olamide.abdulazeez@yahoo.com', '08154543829', '10a, Bola Ahmed Tinubu Way, Igbogbo Ikorodu, Lagos State', NULL, '25', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/OfZGyMuOhvKsoUvnyk1Q2xylF2FIQVWg04S0Xjk9.docx', '<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing to inform you of my interest in seeking opportunities in being a Sales Trainee in your organization . I got informed of the opportunity through a job positing website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I received a B.Sc. with a second class upper division honors from University of Ilorin in 2017 in Marketing. I developed a good interest in Data analysis which i have successfully carried out researches and analyze data which are meant for critical decisions at various business levels. Also i have the skills of identifying new customers and maintaining a profitable business relationships with existing ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to my strong academic background, I have experience working for profit making and various non-profit making organizations where I have acquired skills in strategy development and implementation, decision making, program planning and managing organizational programs, communicating with a diverse group of people effectively and efficiently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I seek interest in this job opportunities as i believe my qualifications fit in and also that will assist me&nbsp; in contributing excellently towards the organizational actualization of her goals and result in developing my career. I will be pleased to know if you would like further information regarding my candidacy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Attached is a copy of my curriculum vitae and I look forward to hearing from you soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abdulquadri Abdulazeez Olamide</p>', NULL, '2020-07-24 13:45:42', '2020-07-24 13:45:42', 3, 'profile_photo/4tUXB2PEEJubwPZrpM3RdTKtgUQhbiS8DbwwAm1G.jpeg', 'profile_video/ye60oB7JqGbSnanMF3FWLhVcr6ba2Tc