(151, 492, 'Loveline Ezenwafor', 'ezenwaforchioma@gmail.com', '08180333175', '16, Oseni street, Surulere, Lagos.', NULL, '23', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/JWcmipe21ufjnyHIIPce1NWFiwTqiAQezFBsxLuw.docx', '<p>&nbsp;I am Loveline Ezenwafor, I recently completed my undergraduate coursework while waiting to be awarded my certificate in Business Administration at Michael Okpara University of Agriculture, Umudike. I am a pending Member of the Nigerian Institute of Management (NIM).<br />\r\nI would like to apply for the position of a sales representative recently advertised by your company on the Jobberman platform.<br />\r\nFrom my enclosed CV, I worked as a sales representative at This &amp; That Supermarket, Lagos before proceeding to study Business Administration in MOUAU.&nbsp;<br />\r\nAt This &amp; That Supermarket, one of my key achievements was that I established, developed and maintained positive business and customer relationships.&nbsp;<br />\r\nI also had the opportunity to be trained on the use of Inventory Management Software and Point of Sales (POS) System.&nbsp;<br />\r\nMy undergraduate studies have also developed my skills in researching a topic, making presentations, storytelling, writing reports and analyzing data.&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo me, sales are more than just selling something, it gives me the opportunity to meet people and make them happy. In a way, sales sort of makes me a problem solver and I, in particular love solving puzzles.&nbsp;<br />\r\nSuccess in the world of Sales, requires perseverance, profit driven focus and exceptionally honed interpersonal skills.&nbsp;<br />\r\nAs an experienced sales representative with a good history in managing customer relationships and drastically increasing sales, I stand in a prime position to significantly contribute to your objectives as your next sales representative.&nbsp;<br />\r\nMy dedication to creating solid and productive relationships with customers along with my steadfast motivation to meet or exceed sales goals characterizes my career accomplishments.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThese skills combined with an urge to work both independently and in a team, I am positioned to exceed your expectations. I look forward to meeting with you to discuss my candidacy in more details. Please, find attached my CV. Thank you for your time and consideration.</p>', NULL, '2020-07-26 00:47:29', '2020-07-26 00:47:29', 3, 'profile_photo/6lKavJrw1bppTw9LpeffPGS7Va7A6pNMpJaEsDB2.jpeg', 'profile_video/CE8AzKNTwhk47CtFbhFvUmXaWotcyXIU1tO9iTMg.mp4'),
