(164, 571, 'Akintomide omoyemi', 'omoyemiakintomide@gmail.com', '08069204266', 'NO 31,AJAGUNNA STREET,OFF ISUTI ROAD, EGAN, IGANDO, LAGOS STATE', NULL, '26', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/7bb42e651232aa896a09445dc5e2bb28.docx', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I, Akintomide Omoyemi Victor, hereby apply for the position as advertised on Social media. The opportunity this vacancy presents will help me in gaining the much needed experience in the Finance market in Nigeria for which I was trained in the prestigious Adeknule Ajasin University Ondo State Nigeria.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My education at an undergraduate level had made me see the immense opportunities of a worthwhile career in the Banking&nbsp; profession which I hope to pursue if given the opportunity to be a part of your reputable firm and contribute my quota in becoming the leading finance providers in Nigeria. I hope to achieve this as a member of your staff who places integrity in forefront of all dealings and has a positive attitude to work, self-motivated, disciplined and able to carry out duties with minimal supervision.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As requested, I hereby enclose my resume and three references along with my application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is my earnest expectation that I get a favourable response and invited for an interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours faithfully,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Akintomide Omoyemi Victor. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-07-29 16:24:59', '2020-07-29 16:24:59', 4, 'profile_photo/ZuAmEsv4NUqb82yj7TXbKhtwGSUNXGKA1k8go0eD.jpeg', 'profile_video/kdrNYDeX5BQbpaL9qsqC26OU20sQJ1IUKFcGD2UL.docx'),
(165, 573, 'Ogbonna Precious', 'ogbonnap16@gmail.com', '08082007788', 'Tonia Emmanuel avenue, peaceland estate, lagos', NULL, '25', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/a803e8342df26bc0df25da5d51e45111.docx', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Madam,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wish to apply for the post of a personal assistant, I felt forced to submit my resume for your review. As an organized and efficient professional with experience providing comprehensive administrative and personal support, I am confident that I would be a valuable asset to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From organizing travel arrangements to managing calendars and schedules, my skillset allows me to thrive in busy environments that let me put my time management and organizational skills to use. Backed by my superior communication and multitasking capabilities, I excel at providing exceptional administrative and staff management expertise and generating optimal productivity and success within businesses and households. Managing extensive support functions including writing correspondence, communicating with multi-functional staff, running errands, and coordinating general household operations while maintaining a consistent level of professionalism and accuracy. Demonstrating dedication to providing outstanding administrative support and meeting deadlines while streamlining operations and facilitating success. Balancing multiple tasks within time-sensitive environments while providing top-level organization and interpersonal skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With my proven commitment to delivering superior assistance , I am more than prepared to extend my record of service to your company. I would appreciate the chance to discuss this position and my qualifications with you further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours sincerely,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ogbonna Precious.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-07-29 19:49:35', '2020-07-29 19:49:35', 3, 'profile_photo/60cRpBxaBlpxPfNh8CcRVEMI6PBNXkVYzVfVZaX9.png', 'profile_vid