(170, 461, 'Olawale Olorundare', 'olorundareolawale@yahoo.com', '08162760556', '41 Road A Close Block 3 Flat 6 Festac Town Lagos', NULL, '30', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/83a4d90a25d900ceed0af603c73c5ecb.docx', '<p>Dedicated, highly-motivated and result-driven sales professional with an accomplished track record to show for it. Exceptional Communicator with a consultative Sales style, strong negotiation skills, exceptional problem-solving abilities and a keen client-needs assessment aptitude. Ability to cultivate strong and sustainable relationships with clients and executive stakeholders to increase company revenue. Strategic planner with a finely-honed implementation skill and a keen eye for details. My expertise includes managing high volume and multiple revenue streams, sales management operations that offer a smooth and efficient services that meets client&rsquo;s expectations. I possess a superb ability to work in a fast-paced environment without direct supervision and also aggressive in identifying opportunities to provide tactical business solutions.</p>', NULL, '2020-07-30 05:43:41', '2020-07-30 05:43:41', 3, 'profile_photo/C3S8ewmNrCjMqaMkaY4TU857nSab6IpYNrpjwCZ9.jpeg', NULL),
(171, 430, 'Ogunleye-Johnson Adebayo', 'believebayo@gmail.com', '+2347037904204', '6, Iroko Awe, Off Ilasan new street, Lekki, Elegushi, Lagos', NULL, '25', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/d018e89d37b13947557e8d0a34bbfee4.pdf', '<p>30th&nbsp;of July, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Human Resource Manager,<br />\r\nSnapnet Nigeria Limited.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Ma,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I write to humbly request for a Five (5) month Pre-service and I.T Internship with your company, Snapnet Nigeria Limited. This decision is to gain the best experience in sales and marketing. In this regard, I intend to familiarize myself with sales and marketing functions and procedures to improve my skills in digital marketing, customer engagements, marketing process flow and advertising.<br />\r\nI am Ogunleye-Johnson Adebayo, a graduate student from the department of Business Administration and Marketing at Babcock University, Ilishan-Remo, Ogun state, awaiting NYSC mobilization. I am a team player with keen interest in company&rsquo;s growth. I hope to be engaged in the day-to-day operations of the sales and marketing department that would broaden my knowledge in my career path and I believe your company Snapnet Nigeria Limited&nbsp;will assist me in achieving these objectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you very much for your kind consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours faithfully,<br />\r\nOgunleye-Johnson, Adebayo</p>', NULL, '2020-07-30 16:44:09', '2020-07-30 17:11:39', 3, 'profile_photo/mSc9vCoTeQMjSVdbK0ijhQUKJPiscvj7qIHWocQY.jpeg', 'profile_video/x6qB6f3fhSlhvvn1MB6W4q6KdJ9AeDhYT5FMC9N7.mp4'),
(172, 582, 'Ojeme Victor', 'ojemeosoria@gmail.com', '08138950213', 'Jagun Olukosi street Okun Ajah Lagos', NULL, '21', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/d367c4c0040b9ac21a69bc3ce36063e6.pdf', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was very excited when I saw your advert for the position of Sales Intern at Snapet Nigeria&nbsp;especially as this is in line with what I am passionate and confident I can deliver on especially with my experience and I have been rigorously trained and tested at Digital Marketing Skill Institute.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am an online marketing professional who has been thoroughly taught by Digital Marketing Skills Institute, Lagos and have done the following projects:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Built my own website. To view visit&nbsp;<a href=\"https://osoriadigital.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://osoriadigital.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Set up and manage Digital marketing Campaigns to generate leads for two dental clinics here in Lagos. To view case study visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/367EaRk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>http://bit.ly/367EaRk</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Built a Website for a dental clinic Lagos. To view visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.firstmobiledentalcare.com.ng/\" target=\"_blank\">www.firstmobiledentalcare.com.ng</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I successfully designed my own e-commerce store</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Increased Foot traffic to a dental clinic via local search engine optimization by helping the clinic to rank on google as the number dentist in Lagos mainland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have also been commended for my good communication skills which have led to increased sales for my clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe I can add value to your organization in the following ways;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Map out your customer sales funnel and craft your customer journey &ndash; from lead generation to sale&nbsp;via paid search, SEO, and PPC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Advice on pillar content pieces for sales pages, ads, social media posts and email sequences using relevant data from Google analytics and other conversion tracking set up on our website to study customer behaviour online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Discover easy list building strategies to grow a following and build your community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Evaluating customer avatar, market conditions and competitor data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please consider, allowing me, create this kind of foundations for your clients as a Digital Marketing Intern at Odigital.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am confident you will find me an exceptional candidate for this position. I invite you to contact me at your earliest convenience to arrange for an interview. Thank you for your time. I look forward to speaking with you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ojeme Victor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-ojeme-6b53b815a/detail/background-image/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-ojeme-6b53b815a/detail/background-image/</a></p>', 'ojemeosoriavictorokunajah_SPC_lagosojemeosoria@gmail_SPC_com08138950213linkedin–ojemevictorprofilesummaryiamconfidentinacceptingchallenges_SPC_resourceful_SPC_knowledgeable_SPC_pro-active_SPC_energeticanddisciplinedindividual_SPC_seekingtoutilizeanddevelopmyskillsandexperiencetocontributeinyourorganization’sgrowth_SPC_iamcommittedandenthusiasticinsolvingcomplexproblemswithcreativethinking_SPC_iamalsopassionateandenjoydigitalmarketingwithabiginterestinsolvingcomplexmarketingproblems_SPC_resultorienteddigitalmarketingprofessionalwiththeabilitytodrivebrandawarenessandrevenuegrowthusingprovendigitalmarketin