(176, 599, 'Obi izunna Christopher', 'chrisizunna3@gmail.com', '08065357762', '29, lucky child road power line ikorodu Lagos', NULL, '27', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/1953babf1453545709abf23160b3fc15.pdf', '<p>I am writing this letter to express my interest in the opening of Solution Sales Executive&nbsp;&nbsp;at your organization.<br />\r\nI have BSc in Cooperative Economic and Management from Nnamdi Azikiwe University, Awka. I have years of experience in Sales . I can offer excellent project-management skills, and a great eye for detail with excellent communication skills, all of which should make me an ideal candidate for this opening.<br />\r\nI have attached my resume for your review. I would welcome the chance to discuss with you on how my skills and strengths can best serve the organization.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThanks</p>', NULL, '2020-08-02 21:16:11', '2020-08-02 21:38:00', 4, 'profile_photo/opUSBp2ihiDk9H54ixpJnD5FKfJ7MZtiWWrMt2Y7.jpeg', 'profile_video/9aTlQoce841x7isDRc4cUhImeVIkWA7EeInFWwaO.qt');
