bsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Benjunior94@outlook.com<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/madam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I write to express my interest for the Solutions Sales Executive&nbsp;role at Snapnet.<strong>&nbsp;</strong>Snapnet, does not only serve to me as the apotheosis of financial companies committed to providing sustainable, cutting-edge solutions to complexities in the industry, but also as an organisation that is committed to providing intensive, top-class training to its employees. The multidisciplinary professional services, diverse teams of talents and values of&nbsp;Snapnet are other things I admire, which attracted me to drop an application,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a vibrant individual, who craves to work in an organisation where I would&nbsp;gain a deeper insight and broaden my knowledge of the financial industry.&nbsp;If given the opportunity, I will, as a matter of course, imbibe the values and culture of Snapnet and exhibit high level of integrity. I am a humble and unassuming gentleman, with a stable temperament, but highly principled. I know how to work politely and professionally with people of different backgrounds and diversities, as I am a man endowed with excellent communication and interpersonal skills, as well as team working and management skills, which would be brought to bear in my dealings with people in your organisation. These skills were indispensable to the success of the technical project I worked on with other team members, each from different backgrounds, for First Bank Nigeria to manage and sell the Bank&rsquo;s mobile banking initiative the first few years it was launched. We achieved amazing results which in turn yielded profits for the bank</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also with my experience in working with two of Nigeria&#39;s biggest banks, my core value, customer satisfaction cannot be overemphasized, and this can only be achieved through excellent customer relations. My job role at the customer experience unit exposed me to various ways to handle customers which is why i have a penchant for excellence, and possess key skills that make me confident in my propensity for being instrumental towards the goals of Snapnet. I am innovative and possess profound numerical, analytical and problem-solving skills, which have helped me maintain excellence throughout my academic career. These skills were critical to the success of various projects assigned to me at Access Bank Nigeria where I worked closely with the customer experience team and I emerged successful after completing numerous assessments and presentations. Similarly, I intend to deploy these skills at your Organisation in performing my duties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, I am a confident, dynamic and strong communicator, with very good presentation and report writing skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Given your company&rsquo;s reputation,&nbsp;I would be honoured if granted an opportunity to be trained and mentored by your well experienced professionals, in order to develop my professional skills and deliver results that will help promote and add value to&nbsp;Snapnet.&nbsp;I believe that the positive attitude, resourcefulness, capacity to learn new skills, and unparalleled passion for success and excellence that I have derived from a variety of my life and work experiences will be vital, and help me create a niche for myself in your organisation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please find enclosed my curriculum vitae for your perusal, while&nbsp;I look forward to a favourable consideration of my application. Thank you for your time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours Sincerely,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umeh Benjamin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', NULL