(184, 606, 'Wuraola Adesikun', 'whuragold10@gmail.com', '08108381894', '5,Ajao estate, Ketu Lagos', NULL, '22', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/54ebd32b21b67b11ddaff777559f973a.docx', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ajao Estate, Ketu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lagos, Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+2348108381894</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wuraolaadesikun@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6th&nbsp;August 2020.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lekki, Lagos Island,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lagos, Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>APPLICATION FOR SOLUTION SALES EXECUTIVE&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When I recently learned about the Snapnet&nbsp;recruitment, I felt compelled to put in for this role as an individual who is interested and learned the principles of Sales, Marketing&nbsp;and Customer Relationship Management. Having built a strong and positive relationship with clients in reference to my past experience, I believe I&rsquo;m a skilled and excellent candidate who is fit for this position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet is a limited company that effectively provides both business and Information technology solutions to clients.&nbsp;As a Sales representative, I have the core&nbsp;values of promoting the sales of the company, and as well,&nbsp;satisfying the target market. Therefore, generating sales and finding solutions to customer&rsquo;s problems are what excite me about this role.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With my negotiating&nbsp;skills and and positive attitude towards my work, I am very best at persuading and as well, satisfying my customers. I am a self-motivated and focused person who pays attention to every detail in order to make my clients content with my service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am highly ambitious and a people-oriented individual with excellent communication and problem-solving skills. I am keen to add good values and also, develop my professional skills at Snapnet Limited&nbsp;and I am available for tests and interviews at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp