(186, 485, 'Thelma Akatah', 'akatahthelma@gmail.com', '08144322055', '12, Sir Sikiru Adewale Street, Sangotedo, Lekki-Ajah, Lagos', NULL, '25', 'female', NULL, 'cv_upload/fe237b4acd2f2610844d886321478f07.docx', '<p>THELMA OMOLADE AKATAH<br />\r\n12, Sir Sikiru Adewale Street, Sangotedo, Lekki-Ajah, Lagos. (234)08144322055. akatahthelma@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7 August, 2020<br />\r\nManager, Human Resources,<br />\r\nSnapnet Nigeria,&nbsp;<br />\r\n1B Abayomi Shonuga Crescent,&nbsp;<br />\r\nLekki Phase 1, Lagos, Nigeria.&nbsp;<br />\r\nDear Sir/Ma<br />\r\nAs a highly skilled and performance-driven individual with exceptional communication and negotiation skills, I am pleased to be applying for the sales intern job at Snapnet Nigeria. Furthermore, I believe that it would be an excellent opportunity for me to grow both personally and professionally and gain more valuable experience.&nbsp;<br />\r\nTo shortly introduce myself, My name is Thelma Akatah and I am a holder of a Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Education and English language which serves as evidence to my exceptional communication skills, both verbal and written, ability to communicate correctly and clearly with all customers, good composition skills-ability to compose a grammatically correct, concise and accurate written response and the ability to work successfully in a team environment as well as independently.<br />\r\nWith my previous employer &ndash;Golden Gate International Academy- I constantly exceeded my targets, and&nbsp; was valued for my ability to deal with complex situations by coming up with unique and fresh solutions. I spent most of my time providing excellent customer service skills, empathizing with and prioritizing clients&rsquo; needs, demonstrating interpersonal skills and worked overtime as required. I had the chance to work as part of a team in order to meet deadlines. This opportunity gave me the chance to gain excellent numerical &amp; analytical skills that are required to work in this industry.<br />\r\nI was also able to sharpen my communication skills which are important when building professional networks both with colleagues and clients. I therefore, welcome the opportunity to work with you in order to build my skills as well as to ensure continuity of your exceptional service to your clients.<br />\r\nI would be delighted to have the opportunity to collaborate with the talented professionals in your Organization. Thank you for your time and for considering my candidacy for the position. I look forward to setting up an interview in the near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind regards,<br />\r\nThelma Akatah</p>', NULL, '2020-08-08 00:53:21', '2020-08-08 00:55:41', 3, 'profile_photo/tsr8ZfbdGnkjFXA4UoBr8xoF87ooYsjjEcBC7CNm.jpeg', 'profile_video/GShQIaDA5bP0vCiYqWArwbzL9UxcI9NWq4IoRnMo.mp4'),
