(188, 611, 'Dorcas Osadare', 'dorcasosadare@gmail.com', '08104553555', '23, Ogunmuyiwa street off johnson busstop ijeshatedo surulere lagos', NULL, '25', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/d1bd17d42745f36c254c34348fc80ba2.jpg', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am applying for a Business Analyst role at Snapet because I strongly believe in the company&#39;s mission to lead technological innovation in Africa and I want to commit to make it a reality. As an accomplished professional with 3+ years of experience analyzing processes and implementing solutions to achieve organizational goals while managing projects throughout all phases, I am confident I will significantly contribute to the objectives of your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I currently consult at Aide agency as a business analyst and I excel at connecting with cross-functional decision makers and acquiring necessary and relevant information to inform and direct goal-oriented business solutions to meet organizational needs. From developing complex use case reports and diagrams and analyzing internal policies and laws to liaising between departments and training and supporting staff, I have acquired the knowledge and experience over the years that will make me excel as a business team member</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Consider the following highlights of my qualifications:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;Ability to analyze a full range of business concerns, needs, and requirements to identify and recommended processes, products, and solutions to meet goals and objectives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;Define, analyze, and achieve business goals while leading projects through all phases from definition through execution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;Reputation for gaining an in-depth understanding of project value and core concerns prior to recommending and implementing effective business solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;Utilize superior communication, leadership, team collaboration, staff training, and time management skills to build consensus across relevant parties and drive business success.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a proven track record of analyzing business processes and leading project management responsibilities, I am positioned to vastly exceed your expectations for this role and any similar one and substantially benefit your organization.&nbsp;Attached is my CV for your review and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your consideration.</p>', NULL, '2020-08-10 18:22:16', '2020-08-10 18:22:16', 3, 'profile_photo/0YluiqLGzmxE6rwW7RGrhlw5DLY2smvtguUJjafD.docx', NULL),
