f serving would give me further exposure and help facilitate my career development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; I have held a summer internship at ALCON Nigeria Limited in Port-Harcourt. During my time there, I shadowed financial analysts in the preparation of financial statements and helped in the physical archiving of these&nbsp; financial&nbsp; documents. Also, I have held a summer internship at CRM Bookshop in Ogun State. I was in charge of the sale of Christian books and bibles and kept records of financial transactions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; I am competent in the use of the Microsoft Office Suite software and possess exceptional interpersonal skills which I believe would make me an asset to your program. After reading the job core values, I am very confident that I can make an immediate and significant contribution to your company&rsquo;s operations, and able to manage multiple priorities at the same time. This would provide me with the ideal opportunity to assist your organization and to expand my skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Kindly refer to the accompanying CV for more detailed information regarding my abilities and skill sets. If this brief account of my competencies intrigues you enough to invite me for an interview, please contact me at your earliest convenience. I appreciate your time and consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;