(220, 725, 'Ayewumi Precious Obakemi', 'ayekemprecious@gmail.com', '07032477276', 'Omoniyi Street Ketu Lagos', NULL, '23', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/43e6b05b2f1c05f89834fa7902f414b6.pdf', '<p>Dear HR Team,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I write in response to the vacancy in your establishment for intersnhip training as published on a local news field days ago.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a fresh&nbsp; graduate, of Obafemi Awolowo University with Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Economics. I am a result driven&nbsp; individual capable of multi-tasking with little or no supervision. I possess excellent oral, written and listening skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since I completed my NYSC program, I have had passion and interest to acquire more profesional certification and qualifications and also keep learning&nbsp; more as to become expert in my field and career. This has driven my action&nbsp; to enrol for professional&nbsp; and self development trainings.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am currently a certified project manager and Strategic content marketer. And I see my self learn more, practice more effectively&nbsp; with this in the marketing and sales world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>07032477276&nbsp;</p>', 'careersummarycommittedindividualadeptinefficientlyutilizingavailableresourcesincompletingassignedtasks_SPC_seekinganentry-levelpositionasafreshgraduateofeconomics_SPC_providingahigh-endadministrativedutyforthecompany_SPC_mycareergoalistousemyskillsandknowledgeinprovidingconsultancyandcounsellingoneconomicandfinancialmatters_SPC_skillshighlightprojectmanagement_SPC_stronganalyticalanddecision-makingskills_SPC_remarkableabilitytoperformresearchforcomplexprojectswitheview_SPC_statisticalanalysis_SPC_microsoftword_SPC_excelandpowerpoint_SPC_marketing_SPC_experiencebusinessdevelopmentmanageratotfashionhub2020managingbusinessgrowththrougheffectiveproductmarketingandmarketanalysis_SPC_responsibleforcreatingnewbusinessleadsandmanagingcustomerrelations_SPC_nationalyouthservicecor