(221, 726, 'Emeka Uchenna Desire', 'uchennadesire4@gmail.com', '07055304124', '6 Onofowakan street, shomolu, Lagos.', NULL, '26', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/11c08dae2ee27907ea6d77fa8336062e.pdf', '<p>To:<br />\r\nHuman Resource Manager,<br />\r\nSnapet ICT Consulting Firm,<br />\r\n1b Abayomi Crescent, Lekki phase 1<br />\r\nLagos State.<br />\r\n15th September 2020.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; Dear Sir/ Madam.<br />\r\nI want to express my interest in the sales internship role in your fast-growing ICT consulting firm. I am a diligent and dynamic young professional with two years of experience in sales, marketing, brand management, account management, and customer service.<br />\r\nI&rsquo;m adept at increasing sales through diligent research and also experienced at managing complex projects. I&rsquo;m a dynamic and creative marketer with uncommon experience in consistently penetrating new markets to ensure sustainable revenue growth. I&rsquo;m a business turn around champion with hand-on experience in ensuring efficient and effective management of clients, business operation, and process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was privileged to work in different capacities, most recent is my role in the Nigerian brewery, as a sales and Marketing trainee where I worked directly with my line manager for strategic planning of different brand activation. My team and I planned strategically for the re-launch of new star drink in mainstream, off-premise, and premium stores which generated sales. I was responsible for the execution of in-bar sales and promotions in different bars. I was privileged to execute a brand promotion in premium stores for the sale of Nigerian brewery drinks in premium stores. I also worked with Citichef&nbsp; Nigeria as an Account Manager. At Citichef, I developed and implemented integrated communications plans for brand awareness across all the social media channels and also increase the visibility of its reputation across a wider audience. The results of these efforts and str