(224, 741, 'Sunday Babatunde, BENJAMIN', 'tundeben09@gmail.com', '08052361749', 'Lagos, Nigeria', NULL, NULL, 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/f72d09941a38362bebaf547d3a1c5fc6.docx', '<p>APPLICATION FOR THE POST OF A DATA SCIENTIST</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;I wish to humbly apply for the post of a data scientist within your establishment.&nbsp;Due to my passion for data-driven environments;&nbsp;I obtained certificates in data science from Johns Hopkins University and Cognitive Class (formerly IBM Big Data University).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;I have just recently completed my virtual internship in the <strong>KPMG data analytics consulting program</strong> (<em><strong>unguided project</strong></em>) where I completed practical tasks in data quality assessment, data insights and data insights presentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; I was required to build a <strong>predictive model</strong> (using customers&rsquo; transactional data) which would then in turn be applied on a new customer data set to determine which ones the client should focus their marketing resources on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I previously worked as a <strong>Market Research Coordinator</strong> where my duties involved coordinating the activities of team members, collecting data on consumers, competitors and the market place. I compile statistical data using modern methods (like SurveyToGo and SurveyCTO) and traditional methods to collect it. I equally analyze data using<strong> R programming</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; I intend to bring all these transferrable experiences to a reputable company like yours while sharpening my skills further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; Thanks in anticipation of your response.<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Yours Faithfully,<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nb