(238, 795, 'Moses Ozoumeh', 'mosesozoumeh@gmail.com', '+2340814405559', '45 Valentine Obasi Street off mingles', NULL, '29', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/6d66f8e4c6f69df61144508f96d84c38.docx', '<p>Dear Sir/Ma, I would love to fill the open salesperson intern position at Snapnet that I read about on LinkedIn. I have 3 years of sales experience under my belt working in technology, Education and Engineering sectors and would like to bring my skills into your company. I have excellent interpersonal skills and the drive to succeed and I regularly persevere to beat all set sales goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe the best method to make sales is not to be pushy or slick, but rather highlight the best features of the product being sold, and have a great listening ability to know when a customer likes a product but want a compromise to buy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Education sector, I chat with school owners prior to showing them the value and benefits of my structured physical education curriculum for kids and then strike a win-win model according to what they have stated they need or want. I have applied this same method in all the industries I have worked as a sales person. I would bring the same care as a salesperson in Snapnet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would as you would want me to in growing the company customer base My great social skills make customers want to purchase. I would really like to be a sales intern at Snapet. I would love to meet the company HR to discuss further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moses Ozoumeh&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-09-30 23:16:29', '2020-09-30 23:16:29', 3, 'profile_photo/2QVxS6LPaQiL9Rp6jRhYD3gR1ZcJpuLKXHNVnxvW.jpeg', 'profile_video/HQB08pKjT58YpVJs8NLvvxIA32iVYWWd2r2ccZmG.mp4'),
