(241, 745, 'Uchechukwu Ikeobi', 'uchechikeobi@gmail.com', '08063027242', '69, Ajose Street, Maryland, Lagos, Nigeria', NULL, '25', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/2e10e25408a1c7abefa2bf05ec848191.pdf', '<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By way of introduction, I am currently wrapping up my M.Sc in Computer Science at the Federal University of Agriculture, Abeokuta, Ogun State. For the past four years, I have focused my career path and academic pursuits on learning and developing relevant skills necessary to deliver effectively in the corporate world. As a personal mission, I strive to solve problems at any level with the design thinking model.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In 2017, I worked on a Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation project, gaining valuable experience and developing skillsets in research and data analysis as I was responsible for capturing and analyzing both quantitative and qualitative data gathered. Working on this project further developed my social awareness and relationship management skills, which are qualities relevant for career exploits. This experience also helped me developed my skills in making presentations, writing reports and decision making using data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additionally, my abilities extend to collaboration and communication with proficiency in teamwork. Working with people from diverse backgrounds in the university environment has provided me with a deep understanding and awareness of differences in both individuals and organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am very excited about this opportunity and look forward to discussing my application with you in greater detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please, review my Resume for additional details regarding my expertise and career achievement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While I look forward to hearing from you and joining this great team of professionals, accept my sincere assurances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warm Regards,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ikeobi, Uchechukwu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+234 806 302 7242</p>', 'ikeobiuchechukwuifeoluwa