(242, 777, 'Blessing Ahisu', 'ahisublessing@gmail.com', '+2348130653660', 'Off Police Barracks, Takur Site, Dutse, Jigawa State.', NULL, '26', 'female', NULL, 'cv_upload/c167c84a7bc4da837ff68b979f7ba373.docx', '<p>Blessing Ahisu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Takur Site</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dutse, Jigawa, 720232</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+2348130653660</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:ahisublessing@gmail.com\">ahisublessing@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>October 1st, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chuma Ukeagu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CEO &amp; Principal Consultant</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet Nigeria Limited</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Chuma Ukeagu,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>APPLICATION FOR THE POSITION OF SALES INTERN</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing in regards to the position of sales intern at Snapnet Nigeria Limited as seen in your Vacancy announcement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Having read through your company`s profile, I admired your organization. I am convinced that your organization will provide a fertile ground for my dreams to flourish. My dream is to work in an environment where I can give my share to the promotion of a world that make use of software solutions to solve real life problems and to also grow my skills and values in a rich technological environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My past experiences as a Front Desk Manager at an IT firm during my industrial training have exposed me to building a friendly relationship with clients and visitors. I also had the opportunity to participate in a software development training on programming with Coldfusion markup language and MySQL. In addition, I was trained on how to make use of some of the software solutions developed by the organization such as .CONNECT EDUCATOR ( a school management software), .CONNECT FINANCE, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prior to the end of my NYSC program I had the privilege to work as a data entry clerk at a non-governmental organization. The experiences I had exposed me to the various ways of gathering data as well as entering data in databases and maintaining accurate records of &nbsp;company&rsquo;s valuable &nbsp;information. I have also served as an attendant during meetings with various stakeholders from the public and private sectors and have successfully handled their issues/concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recently I applied for the Google Africa Developer Scholarship 2020 program and I am delighted to be among the learners that were selected for android track. By means of the program, I have learnt about how to implement some concepts in Android Development such as making a network request using Retrofit, working with google forms, view pager, Recyclerview, SQLite, JSON, Git and GitHub and so on. I look forward to becoming one of the learners that will be selected to participate in the Google Certified Associate Android Developer examination.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although I studied Computer Science, I have worked with my mother in her business for many years and I&nbsp;have been able to develop some&nbsp;sales and marketing skills such as how to build and maintain a good relationship with clients, how to speak persuasively to them, how to negotiate with clients, and so on. Also, I strongly feel and hope that the enthusiasm I used in working for NGOs, coupled with the knowledge and experiences I have acquired, over the years, and as a graduate of Computer will be very useful in playing the role of a Sales Intern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have uploaded my CV as required, for your consideration. I would be available for an interview to provide any additional information you may be interested in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you very much, in advance, for your time in reviewing my application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best regards,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Blessing Ahisu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-10-01 23:01:59', '2020-10-02 00:01:02', 3, 'profile_photo/xLZwCsk0vQUSbyeBLumu6cElqbexi7JM1KA9WvBr.jpeg', 'profile_video/rlvt88qVRUQOPvrMAX3K4NLgoqNt2WJZ2D6K8Ctg.mp4'),
