(245, 810, 'Choko stamley', 'chokostanley1990@gmail.com', '07065335965', 'Ape express way lekki by chevron junction', NULL, '29', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/cb1d0f5b980b033aa6d843a1f302e24a.docx', '<p>To the HR,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6th October, 2020.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear sir/Ma,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nI recently saw an advertisment for Sales&nbsp; Marketer. I am very keen on the position and this letter is an expression of my interest in the vacancy.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nIf you are looking for a candidate who is analytical and management oriented, helpful and has bags on initiative, then look no further. I have worked as a sales executive&nbsp; in a real estate organization, a financial institution(03 capital Nigeria Ltd), in a cosmetic giant company as an inventory officer, my industrial training in an international oil company (Total E&amp;P ), and I offer a combination of unique skills and competencies which I developed through a lengthy and rewarding career. I have honed human relationship, negotiation, and data analysis skills while proficient in critical thinking. In previous roles, I have contributed to organisational improvements, collaborative team efforts and attainment of key business targets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please review my attached resume for a more detailed account of my abilities and skills. I sincerely believe that with the skills I have gained in my previous work I can make a tremendous contribution to your existing team.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>yours sincerely,&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Choko Stanley,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>07065335965.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-10-07 01:03:36', '2020-10-07 01:03:36', 3, 'profile_photo/S5yrNt5Z3WPlejOjqFsPbIIPLxP47YNhLcTaModf.jpeg', NULL),
(246, 812, 'Yovoyan Abraham Viyon', 'yovoyan.abraham@yahoo.com', '+2348160903659', '36, Ajah, Along Lekki-Epe Expressway, Lagos, Nigeria.', NULL, '26', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/2f77790116cafd1f09cc2a1a04f7309c.pdf', '<p>Hiring Manager</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Hiring Manager:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a lover of technology and its transformative potential to enterprises and businesses, I am very delighted to express my keen interest in the Sales Intern position. I will be offering my demonstrated willingness to learn, experience, skills and knowledge in information technology from my previous engagements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I enrolled in Unites Virtual Cisco Academy Program on Cybersecurity. This was as a result of my quest for knowledge and to improve myself for impact.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I understand what it means to work in a very fast paced environment and turn over results within tight timelines. This was demonstrated while performing simulation in the test systems, conducting documentations, self-training and integration/user acceptance testing on a software enhancement package (EHP8) project using HP ALM (Application Lifecycle Management).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have learnt the importance of sustaining a learning mindset and applying it to surmount challenges. I implemented the process of design thinking to identify the business pain point alongside my colleagues. We did our internet research and applied our findings to develop a solution which saved Shell Nigeria USD33,000.00 in cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have successfully handled challenging situations in the past and made reckonable impacts as a result. I do up-skill myself using several learning platforms such as LinkedIn Learning and YouTube videos among others. I will love to know more about Snapnet and understand how I will be able to contribute to advancing the business impacts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you.</p>', '1yovoyanabrahamviyon36_SPC_ajah_SPC_alonglekki-epeexpressway_SPC_lagos•(+234)816090