(247, 813, 'EJIKE STEPHEN IGWE', 'ejikestephen42@gmail.com', '08036135958', 'No 10 Church Street, Gbagada, Lagos State', NULL, '30', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/63fdbbcec6c1f75085ec3af6f64a5faa.pdf', '<p>Ejike Stephen Igwe<br />\r\nNo. 10 Church Street, Gbagada, Lagos State, Nigeria.<br />\r\n+2348036135958, +2349059576911<br />\r\nejikestephen42@gmail.com, ejike.igwe@aun.edu.ng&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>October 8, 2020.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Human Resource Manager,<br />\r\nSnapnet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>APPLICATION FOR THE POSITION OF DATA SCIENTIST&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This letter is in regards to my interest in applying for the position of a Data Scientist recently advertised on Jobberman.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From my experience as an accomplished technical officer, I regularly use my exceptional skills to act as a technical liaison between management and the IT department.&nbsp;<br />\r\nIn my last position as an ICT Officer, I was responsible for generating weekly updates for the management and monitor a large technology transition project. I developed and maintain the company&rsquo;s website using my skills in web design and also using the power of social media of different platforms to promote the company&rsquo;s products and services. There was an unceasingly attraction of more customers to the industry and thus increased sales and ease of doing business as customers can order their products online and make enquiries with no stress. The positive feedback received from the management and clients were amazing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Working as an IT support representative, I was responsible for drafting the company&rsquo;s correspondence, preparing data reports for management, handling and directing calls/emails, organising company meetings/off-site events and providing customer support for clients with technical related issues. My ability to work with all levels of management and my skills in training personnel makes me an invaluable asset. My exceptional teamwork and communication skills, who always gets the job done comes from my ability to work cross-functionally and multi-task various responsibilities. Knowledge of cutting-edge technology is the result of my years of experience and research.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My command of corporate computer technology makes me an ideal candidate for your organisation and my experience will make an extensive impact in your organisation, as an individual who is continuously inspired to break my limits, aims to achieve more and gain more skills to improve in my operational performance. I trust my qualification and your needs would be an excellent fit. I look forward to sharing with you my professional experience and setting up a personal interview at your convenience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for your consideration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSincerely,<br />\r\nEjike Stephen Igwe.</p>', '1ejikestephenigwe|personalinformationejikestephenigweno10churchstreet_SPC_gbagada_SPC_lagosstate_SPC_nigeria_SPC_+2348036135958+2349059576911ejikestephen42@gmail_SPC_com_SPC_ejike_SPC_igwe@aun_SPC_edu_SPC_ngworkexperiencefeb2018–june2020icthelpdeskmanagercewopilimited_SPC_abakaliki(nigeria)▪managetheoveralltechnologyinfrastructureincludingplanning_SPC_implementation_SPC_andmanagethesoftwareandhardwareinfrastructuretosupportoperations_SPC_▪providerelevanttechnologyrelatedservicessuchassupportandcontributiontoit-relatedtasksorprojectsthroughtheimplementationofappropriatetechnologiesandsolutions_SPC_▪providestafftrainingoncommonbusinessapplicationsanduseofcomputersystems_SPC_▪administrateandensurethemaintenanceofthecompany\'ssystems_SPC_including:generalcomputersupport_SPC_softwareinstallationsandupdates_SPC_licensemanagement_SPC_databaseadministration_SPC_network_SPC_printers_SPC_audio/videoconferencingandmobilephonesupport_SPC_feb2017–dec2017ittechnicalsupportofficerministryofict_SPC_calabar(nigeria)▪installationandconfigurationofcomputerhardware_SPC_operatingsystemsandapplications_SPC_▪monitorandm