(248, 362, 'Ezekiel Ibegbunam', 'ezekielibe@hotmail.com', '08036614100', '5 Jasper Ike Street, Lekki Phase 1', NULL, '29', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/07d97a2c7614609d9d5ca39da17b6d3e.pdf', '<p><strong>Ezekiel Ibegbunam</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto:ezekielibe@gmail.com\">ezekielibe@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>October 8, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet Nigeria Limited</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1b Abayomi Shonuga Crescent, Lekki Phase 1, Lagos Nigeria</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RE: Data Scientist</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please accept this letter as an expression of my interest in Data Scientist position at Snapnet Nigeria Limited, a prestigious and reputable name in innovative technology. I am confident in my ability to perform as a Data Scientist at Snapnet Nigeria Limited due to my viable education and work experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My work experience is back up with the series of projects I have carried out as a Data Scientist with Quantium and KPMG, with reference to the aforementioned statement is my Data Science portfolio website at (<a href=\"http://www.ezekielibe.github.io\">www.ezekielibe.github.io</a>) in which I had an extensive range of responsibilities including;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Selecting features, optimizing classifiers, data mining, expanding the company&rsquo;s data, improving data collection techniques, pre-processing data and doing ad-hoc analyses such as predictive modelling and experimentation.</li>\r\n	<li>Crafted algorithms using Python to filter data collection results</li>\r\n	<li>Developed and followed standard operating procedure for verifying data integrity, following CRISP-DM (Cross Industry Standard Process for Data Mining) methodology.</li>\r\n	<li>Created data visualization graphs and charts to make meaning of data for data value chain stakeholders.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Amongst what I have accomplished is Customer Centric Award (2018) with a Tier-1 Gold Partner 