(249, 817, 'Oluwaseun Asifat', 'asifatoluwaseun@yahoo.co.uk', '09093790661', 'No 154, Iju Road, Ifako Ijaiye, Lagos', NULL, NULL, 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/bcf5ddff6ccd883cb344e47382964f06.doc', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Having elevated the performance and profitability of diverse organizations through expert alignment of innovative Brand Management, Marketing, and Sales strategies, I am writing to offer your company more than 7 years of experience in creative development/leadership of promotional and educational campaigns. With expertise in the Outdoor, Lifestyle, and brand marketing, my background includes front end experience selling and marketing to millennial. As a reputable contributor to increased sales and visibility for organizations, I am confident in my abilities to generate superior results for your company as Brand Communicator.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a visionary leader who utilizes &ldquo;out of the box&rdquo; strategies to spark ideas that generate growth. I offer years of diversified experience and the ability to inspire trust among stakeholders. My roles in the past ranged from Event Manager, Manchester Utd FC Head, Sales &amp; Teksight Brand Communicator, and Head of Business Strategy. I have achieved significant results by identifying process improvements and implementing strategic sales and marketing strategies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A sample of key contributions includes</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I worked with my team to drive the experiential engagement of Customers for TRANSSION GROUP (INFINIX, TECNO and ITEL) which yielded 26% increase for the business across board.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a detail oriented individual with a passion for excellence, I am adept at listening to client&rsquo;s needs, then analyzing and implementing the best designed solution. I have devoted my career to developing winning marketing strategies, boosting brand awareness, and positively impacting businesses and communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please accept this cover letter and enclosed resume as an introduction to my skills and background. For a more detailed presentation of my offerings, feel free to contact me at your earliest convenience to schedule a conference. Thank you in advance for your consideration and I look forward to our conversation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oluwaseun Asifat</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>09093790661</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2020-10-12 18:33:03', '2020-10-12 18:33:03', 3, 'profile_photo/sJa0liBOh6ssOkt00Xoma7ezj7VamAuBbDipW70V.png', NULL),
