(320, 888, 'Anthony Ikemefuna', 'aikemefuna3@gmail.com', '+2348169623983', '9, Muftau Shobola, Haruna, Ifako Ijaye', NULL, '25', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/70e3f749da4f9f996c1d6b661790044b.docx', '<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enclosed you will find my resume, which I am remitting in response to your recent post for a back-end software developer for your company. I bring a solid 2 plus years&rsquo; experience in this field and feel that my accomplishments and qualifications as a developer will benefit the position you are offering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am proficient in c#, html/css,&nbsp; and sql server and have experience with web api&#39;s, javascript, ajax and .net core. My attention to detail, communication and time management skills have proven beneficial to various software and systems development projects for business in such areas as education, energy, estate and hotel management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following lists highlights some of my&nbsp; professional successes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. I was among a two man team of software developers that revamped a school management system, FLEXSCHOOL,&nbsp; designed and developed with the latest .netcore&nbsp; technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Modeled, designed and developed an enterprise system, EasyVend. EasyVend is an all in one solution for Estate Management. Some of its features includes; Prepaid meter vending, Customer management, Bills Collections, Visitor Managment, Meter management, Messaging system etc. (<a href=\"https://www.easyvend.ng\">https://www.easyvend.ng</a>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Developed the backend api for the Easyvend Mobile app. Listed on playstore as Easyvend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Among a two man team of software developers that designed a Learning Management System (<a href=\"http://ats.thecitadelglobal.org\">http://ats.thecitadelglobal.org</a>), ATS ONLINE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5. Developed the web service that powers a learning management system mobile app. ATS Online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6. I led a team of developers to develop a Bulk Messaging System, Flex SMS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7. I led a team of developers to build a Mini banking application best suitable for co-operative societies, COOPMAN.<br />\r\nPrior experience has enabled me to build strong management and organizational skills that I will continue to apply to the back-end software developer position at your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have demonstrated a consistent ability to bring projects from design to implementation within time and budget constraints while providing effective applications and ensuring customer satisfaction. I am available to further discuss this position and my qualifications at a time of your convenience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best Regards</p>', NULL, '2020-10-24 00:38:38', '2020-10-24 00:38:38', 1, 'profile_photo/ZK88zZW6lktBmg2FjFhZkO50QzCvytsTR09MzhqJ.jpeg', NULL),
(321, 891, 'Aadam Bodunrin', 'aadamolalekan@gmail.com', '08058024304', '7, Oluwaseun Yekini Close, Gloryland Estate, Arepo,', NULL, '26', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/168e80d98e5e249ab7777fad526d21ef.pdf', '<p>Hello,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I read with great interest your advert for the role of Data Scientist, which was advertised via your company&#39;s website. I am applying for this position because it offers me the challenges that my educational qualifications and experience have prepared me to handle on a professional level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a graduate of Agricultural Economics from the University of Ibadan. I have also acquired several other skills after obtaining my degree in December 2016, which includes Data Analytics, amongst other skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs a Digital Strategist at QVT media for twelve months, I ensured that its clients received the best of Data-led strategies. The likes of Premium Pension and FMN received cost-effective media plans and achieved their business objectives. &nbsp;I am an agile learner who loves to participate in knowledge sharing. After undergoing the Data Analytics program at UTIVA, I trained eleven (11) of my colleagues on how to visualize data with Microsoft Power BI.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am fluent in several data management systems and software, including Microsoft Excel, SQL (Postgres), Azure Data Studio, and Python. I am currently a data science fellow with the&nbsp;information and data analytics foundation, where I have learned a lot about producing production-ready products and &nbsp;Machine learning algorithms. I recently became Microsoft Certified- Azure Data Scientist Associate as part of my quest to become a world-class data scientist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My attached resume and certificates on soft-skills like emotional intelligence and design thinking will tell you more about how I am a good fit for this role.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On a personal level, I am detail-oriented, organized, independent, composed, and highly d