(323, 893, 'Olubukunwa Osinowo', 'osinowobukunwa@gmail.com', '+2348062142303', '3, Salvation Street, Bale Akinosi town, Ajuwon, Lagos state.', NULL, '25', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/9c04eb1ba753f5e3dfea4e2d6a842ac5.pdf', '<p><a href=\"mailto:osinowobukunwa@gmail.com\">osinowobukunwa@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>+234-806-214-2303</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3, Salvation Street, Bale Akinosi town, Ajuwon, Lagos state.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>October 23, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Human Resources Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet Nigeria Limited,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1b Abayomi Shonuga Crescent, Lekki Phase 1, Lagos Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing in response to your online job posting for a Data Scientist at Snapnet Nigeria Limited which I saw on LinkedIn. Upon further research on Snapnet and its solution-oriented, qualitative services and outlook, I thought this position would be a good fit for a problem solver like myself who is actively looking to deliver beauty and functionality to businesses and other entities via data analytics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My engineering background speaks to my strong mathematical problem solving and modelling skills as well as my solid grasp of statistics and numerical analysis in general. I am fairly good with Python for data analysis (mining, cleaning, regrouping, drawing invaluable insights, interfacing with SQL workbenches, visualizing, creating linear predictive models, etc.), using the relevant data analysis related libraries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have always had an analytical mind which I have put to use in my professional history, while working with Schlumberger, in the storage and tracking of Wireline logging tools and more recently, as a maintenance engineer with the Ministry of Works. You can also observe from my resume, my aptitude to deliver excellent results, take initiative, communicate perspicaciously and learn fast and eagerly. I