(324, 185, 'Victor Momodu', 'momoduvictor1@gmail.com', '07034146393', '45, Nathaniel Osagie Avenue, Ikorodu Rd, Lagos, Nigeria', NULL, '21', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/96ab61024e4014731851c07e24ca6e9f.docx', '<p>To</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hiring Manager</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapnet Limited,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1B Abayomi Shonuga Crescent, Lekki Phase 1, Lagos Nigeria</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of my greatest passions is value creation which is evident in my Data Scientist role at Octave Analytics, as well as my dedication to continuous career development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have worked on various wide-ranging projects especially in the financial sector which have allowed me to expand my data toolbox and hands-on expertise. These experiences have given me a deep understanding of the complexities of data, including customer analytics, product analytics, data mining, data profiling, deployment of business risk models to evaluate competitive business strategies and data science project management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recently, I have been working with two (2) financial institutions in Nigeria, E-tranzact and Coronation Merchant Bank on a Data Analytics &amp; BI Reporting Project. Having 100% client satisfaction ratings, I am positive I am the ideal candidate for the Data Scientist position on the team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During my work on various projects, I have had some remarkable accomplishments:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Slashed customer churn rate by 40% by applying business risk models which increased revenue by 8%.</li>\r\n	<li>Identified opportunities with data profiling which activated 10% of high-profit customers by deploying data science models and building advanced analytics dashboards to track customer patterns.</li>\r\n	<li>Developed a new automation framework for a series of reports, thus reducing processing time in general by 65%.</li>\r\n	<li>Automated the ETL and data warehousing process which accelerated data integration cycles by 75%. Furthermore, data integrity was accelerated by 85% by ETL/BI testing of constructed data architectures which aligns with the business requirements.</li>\r\n	<li>Revamped system processes and recommended data governance policies which improved data quality by 60%.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe I possess the versatile skillset and professional experience to contribute to the vision of Snapnet in providing innovative solutions which meets client satisfaction. If given the chance to transfer my expertise to Snapnet, I will contribute to the company&rsquo;s success with that same commitment and drive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I love what Snapnet sets to achieve and it will be my pleasure to be a part of adding value with world-class solutions generated from an ecosystem of brilliant minds that exist in this organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would love the opportunity to discuss your most ambitious business goals and demonstrate how my past wins can easily translate over to Snapnet for increased revenue and management systems improvement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking forward to your positive response.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Victor.</p>', NULL, '2020-10-24 17:03:18', '2020-10-24 17:03:18', 5, 'profile_photo/P34vphZs9nelDyR79LvQpfPAYFmHu54pRWjs2HGm.png', NULL);
