(325, 894, 'Yusuf Emmanuel', 'emmanuelyusuf62@yahoo.com', '07036809129', NULL, NULL, '26', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/037c67c638292371c2143f6a23c3f3e4.pdf', '<p>Dear Hiring Manager,<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nI am writing to apply for the position of a Financial Analyst in your firm. As an experienced Accountant with more than three years&rsquo; experience in investment banking, data analysis and financial analysis for several companies, I am confident that my skills make me a strong candidate to fulfill your company&rsquo;s needs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a fund accountant at ARM investment managers, I built and maintained trust with senior stakeholders at various organizational levels and presented complex topics while facilitating and delivering actionable insights to solve problems and make decisions. I successfully standardized the automation of the reporting system and loan administration system, worked with back and frontend developers, designers, and marketing strategists to define and develop the reporting infrastructure for end-user&rsquo;s ease of use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Superflux International Ltd, I generated a one-time Microsoft script using python to support the daily cashflow report which usually delayed management decision making process. My contribution helped develop a faster and precise method of reporting that aid with fact-based culture through continuous improvement, which ultimately permitted senior management to make better informed data-driven decisions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI&nbsp;am a highly effective communicator, adept at translating complex messages simplistically to diverse audiences, and I have strong interpersonal skills, empathy, and integrity. I am fluent in English, Spanish, and French.<br />\r\nI look forward to hearing from you at your earliest convenience.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Emmanuel Akorede Yusuf</p>', NULL, '2020-10-24 17:22:32', '2020-10-24 17:22:32', 4, 'profile_photo/OLzU348PieyvMyPzfEHTSWJ4gniXlUC4qdl7IuHN.png', NULL),
(326, 895, 'CHRISTIAN CHINWEIKE UKACHUKWU', 'chinweikeukachukwu@gmail.com', '+2348130058260', '7 Modinatu Obaremi Street', NULL, '27', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/8cbb62973172dc2f13b89d490531b116.pdf', '<hr />\r\n<p><strong>CHRISTIAN CHINWEIKE UKACHUKWU</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>No 7 Modinatu Obaremi Street, Ogba, Ikeja, Lagos Nigeria</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tel: +2348130052860&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Email:chinweikeukachukwu@gmail.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.github.com/kokovariax\">GITHUB</a>&nbsp; <a href=\"http://www.rpubs.com/kokovariax\">RPUBS</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gitlab.com/kokovariax\">GITLAB</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>24th October, 2020</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for this opportunity to apply for the role of Data Analyst in your company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As business decisions made out of data driven insights promote growth and sustainability of a society&rsquo;s economy, I have devoted myself to acquisition and development of analytical skills&nbsp;to enable me make great impacts in business research and development. I had the privilege of working for the Department of Petroleum Resources, where I gained the experience of monitoring crude oil trade from three swamp area terminals. I lead a team that designed a macro-powered excel system that enables quick and accurate oil stock verification thereby reducing the ship/shore cargo volume difference to the barest minimum. My recent role as Business Analyst in a Cloud-Based company exposed me to the use of data storytelling to make sound and research driven suggestions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a degree in Petroleum Engineering and with skills acquired from training and proven experience in different aspects of research and data analytics like: Data toolbox, Data Acquisition and cleaning, Data visualization, Statistical inferences and Prediction Models, and Data Presentation from Johns Hopkins University through Coursera, I hope to function well beyond expectations in this role. Fascinated also by business intelligence, I have also acquired&nbsp;some essential skills in supply chain management and SAP Business Essentials with major focus on Business One and Fiori 3 to enhance my cooperate management skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a resourceful, teachable and diligent young man with proven good communication skills. My business initiative is dominant and I am driven by research and innovation, keen to details and capable of novel ideas. I hope to leverage the above skills in my duties and to ensure excellent business suggestions. After reviewing my attached CV, I hope you will find me a suitable candidate for this role. I look forward to hearing from you soon and elaborating upon how my specific skills would benefit Snapnet. Thank you</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yours sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ukachukwu Christian Chinweike</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+2348130058260</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/christian-ukachukwu\">Linkedin</a></p>', 'www_SPC_github_SPC_com/kokovariaxwww_SPC_linkedin_SPC_com/in/christian-ukachukwuchristianchinweikeukachukwuchinweikeukachukwu@gmail_SPC_com+2348130058260careerobjectives:buildinganexpertiseinhuman_SPC_energyandnaturalresourcesmanagementforbothpersonalandsocietaldevelopment_SPC_throughresearchandefficientdataanalysis_SPC_personaldatadateofbirth20thmay_SPC_1993maritalstatussinglenationalitynigerianlanguagesspokenenglishandigbo(fluent)_SPC_french(basic)educationinstitutionqualificationdate(scope)federaluniversityoftechnology_SPC_owerri_SPC_imostate_SPC_b_SPC_eng_SPC_petroleumengineering(2ndclasshons_SPC_upperdivision)2016pioneersecondaryschool_SPC_umuchu_SPC_anambrastatessce(neco)2005-2011workexperiencexagnetconsultsbusinessdevelopmentanalyst(remote):june2018-date·designedandimplementeddataintegrityandsecurityprotocolsoncloudandprem_SPC_·usedofbitoolstoget(power-bi_SPC_excel_SPC_bigquery)insightsfromdataforgoodbusinessdecisions·createdmlmodelswithpython_SPC_randautomloncloudandprem_SPC_·designedandimple