(327, 898, 'Mubaraq Mayowa Oyeyemi', 'mubaraq.oyeyemi@gmail.com', '08106113882', '56 Olonode Street, Yaba, Lagos', NULL, '24', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/40bd762a03a1820e39d5fa97b3588fae.pdf', '<p>Dear Team,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My name is Mubaraq Mayowa Oyeyemi, a first-class graduate of Mathematics from the University of Ilorin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a Data Science Enthusiast who is actively looking for a Data Scientist role to generate actionable insight from datasets to help your organization achieve its goals. I can analyze large datasets and generate useful pattern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have completed various online courses from renowned websites like Coursera, Udacity, and Dataquest with a keen interest in Data Science and Machine Learning. Using these platforms, I have worked on various projects which involves Supervised Classification, Deep Learning with Tensorflow, and also Unsupervised Learning for customer segmentation. I also have the required knowledge of python and packages like Numpy, Pandas and Scikit-Learn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I possess good presentation skills with knowledge of the financial sector and economy. I am also a startup enthusiast who is massively interested in how technology is disrupting the economy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Having looked at the requirements of your company, I am encouraged to apply for this position and confident of adding value to your organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I look forward to hearing from you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regards</p>', 'mubaraqmayowaoyeyemi56_SPC_olonodestreet_SPC_yaba_SPC_lagosstate_SPC_4june_SPC_1996+234(0)8106113882_SPC_+234(0)8185346200mubaraq_SPC_oyeyemi@gmail_SPC_comcareerobjectives:highlymotivatedrelationshipofficerseekinganewroleasdatascientist/machinelearningengineertohelporganizationachieveitsgoalsthroughdata_SPC_educationuniversityofilorin_SPC_ilorin_SPC_nigeria_SPC_2012-2016b_SPC_sc_SPC_mathematics(firstclass)employmentrecord:dategradepositionorganizationsept2018-presentexecutivetraineerelationshipofficer_SPC_privatebanking_SP