(339, 915, 'Adesola Aanuoluwapo Grace', 'adesolaaanuoluwapograce@gmail.com', '0903 052 5572', '12 Idowu street, Ilaje, Bariga', NULL, '21', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/b11b400a94dab8053f8203251d6bd7cd.pdf', '<p>Dear Sir,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a longtime fan of Scapnet services, I was thrilled&nbsp; to be employed as an entry-level data analyst. With my IT background as well as a dedicated fan of your data services, I know I can use my skill set and knowledge to quickly become a valuable member of the Scapnet team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In my former role in Smart Clinic hospital IT solutio ns, I numerous responsibilities and achievements which would serve me well in this entry-level role at Snapnet company. I&rsquo;m proud to have been on a team which pioneered some innovative new IT best practices. On top of that, my dedication and readiness to work brought about a lot of changes and advancement to the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Obtaining the IT research position at Snapnet would be a digital dream come true. You see, Snapnet&#39;s services has greatly increased my fondness for Data analysis. As such, there is no other firm that would make me as happy to work for. I know that, should I be granted the analyst position, I&rsquo;d be the envy of my circle of friends!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would welcome the chance to discuss your current tech and growth objectives and show you how my successes at university and my previous place of work can translate into the growth of&nbsp; Snapnet. Thank you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Yours faithfully,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Adesola Aanuoluwapo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '12_SPC_idowustreet_SPC_ilaje-barigashomolu_SPC_lagosstate_SPC_+2349030525572adesolaaanuoluwapograce@gmail_SPC_comadesolaaanuoluwapograces