(340, 903, 'Amarachi Anyim', 'amarachi.anyim00@gmail.com', '+2348171931424', '16 Alhaja Alake Street, Bariga, Lagos', NULL, '21', 'female', 'single', 'cv_upload/f3566992bf354be2fb4343d9f69de2ec.pdf', '<p>I am a data scientist, passionate about using technology to effectively and efficiently fulfil demands, drive outstanding customer value and facilitate financial success in an organization. I constantly try to develop creative robust problem-solving skills and experience in creating solutions for organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nDuring my stay in school, I was active in volunteer organizations. Over time, I have had the opportunity to work in teams, developing leadership and people skills to deal with people from different classes and backgrounds. I have taken several online courses and worked on some personal Data Science projects linked to my CV to learn and improve myself.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I motivate myself from the sense of accomplishment I get when I can finally create the interactive visualizations to draw insights or build that model which gave me a tough time. I am happy when I see that my work counts. I am also curious to know how everything is going around me and paying attention to details with a focus on quality service to clients. In my previous place of work as a finance manager, I assessed and managed risks while taking decisions in the organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nI am a proactive and flexible problem-solver. I am also deadline driven and manage my time effectively and efficiently. I am committed to the highest standards of professionalism in the industry and integrity is one of the values dearest to me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for taking the time to review my application. I look forward to speaking with you.</p>', 'okparanelsonseniorsoftwaredeveloper_SPC_imaginebusinessservicescell:+2348030659872email:nelson_SPC_o@imaginebusiness_SPC_com_SPC_ngobodugoraphaelsoftwareengineer_SPC_baobabpartnerscell