(345, 929, 'OLUWATOBI FADOKUN', 'tofad055@gmail.com', '07067352264', 'Block 38 Fidiso Estate, Ibeju Lekki', NULL, '35', 'male', 'married', 'cv_upload/0c3d2d7d34c13cca9e0530349ad4d0b7.docx', '<p>Head,<br />\r\nHuman Resources,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\nDear Sir/Ma,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThanks for the opportunity to apply for the&nbsp; PRE-SALES ENGINEER-LAGOS role at your company. After reviewing your Career Overview, it&rsquo;s clear that you&rsquo;re looking for a candidate that is extremely familiar with the responsibilities associated with such roles, and can perform them confidently. Given these requirements, I am certain that I have the necessary skills to successfully do the job adeptly and perform above expectations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;I am an efficient professional who has been consistently praised as diligent by my co-workers and management. Over the course of my over 8-years career, I&rsquo;ve developed a skill set directly relevant to the&nbsp; PRE-SALES ENGINEER-LAGOS role am applying for, including desktop technology, end user support, and other emerging cloud technologies, etc. Overall, I have consistently demonstrated teamwork, technical, and multitasking abilities in every aspect of my Network Support Engineer role at Rexxys System, and I invite you to review my detailed achievements in the attached Curriculum Vitae.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After reviewing my Curriculum Vitae, I hope you will agree that I am the type of competent and competitive candidate you are looking for. I look forward to elaborating on how my specific skills and abilities will benefit your organization. Please contact me on 07067352264 or via email at tofad055@gmail.com to arrange for a convenient meeting time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks for your kind consideration, and I look forward to hearing from you soon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regards<br />\r\nFadokun Oluwatobi</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N/B: Attached is my Curriculum Vitae</p>', NULL, '2021-02-04 18:33:37', '2021-02-04 18:33:37',