(346, 930, 'Christian Oragui', 'christianoragui@outlook.com', '08053159926', '40B Community road, New Site Estate, Ijegun-Imore, Satellite Town, Lagos, Nigeria', NULL, '26', 'male', 'single', 'cv_upload/6db3df430f052a808f6ff613f0f7a0ef.pdf', '<p>I am a Business Intelligence Developer who also doubles as a Data Insights enthusiast. I utilize Microsoft Power BI product stack in discovering and visualizing patterns in data to produce meaningful insights to drive a positive, growth encapsulated decision-making process. I am also familiar with Microsoft Big Data Cloud Services, Microsoft Azure services, Office 365 product stack, Microsoft Dynamics 365 CRM and Tableau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am conversant with the entire sales cycle in proposing the value proposition of Snapnet&rsquo;s solutions and&nbsp;how they can help our customers monetize their business better and improve their operations. I have led, managed and provided multiple technical responses to RFIs, RFQs, RFPs, and other customer requests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will be very glad to take on this role as a Solution Sales Executive and led Pre Sales&nbsp;at the Abuja branch.</p>', NULL, '2021-02-05 04:17:49', '2021-02-05 04:17:49', 5, 'profile_photo/WvymH1KwjOr89NOtIUXYpcg1PBLS4IyJAQ4rV4gk.jpeg', NULL),
(347, 932, 'Mathias Eze', 'kachiezemat@yahoo.co.uk', '08030983371', 'Plot 2 Ekoroko Estate', NULL, '37', 'male', NULL, 'cv_upload/a31f390c6adf79440915d4238944488d.docx', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapchat Ltd</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abuja ,Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>05/02/2021.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear Human Resources Manager,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am writing this letter and enclosing my resume to apply for the Solution Sales Executive. This position came to my attention through your website job post. After reviewing my resume, I strongly believe I am a qualified candidate for this position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I have Bachelor degree in Mass Communication with strong analysis skill and strategic planning abilities. After research of your company, I feel my goals and values match those of Snapchat Ltd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am ready to take up new challenges with a great team in Snapchat Ltd, Abuja and for over 14 years I have built competencies in Business development, sales and marketing and am seeking to add value to another organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for taking time to review my resume. I look forward to hearing from you to set up an interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eze Onyedika &nbsp;Mathias</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2021-02-05 20:33:07', '2021-02-05 20:56:00', 3, 'profile_photo/5AOHpIG65m8Uauf6OMVuN86AqEMMHdwDyZID9M3i.jpeg', NULL),
