n\r\n<p>Abuja.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dear HR,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RE: APPLICATION FOR THE POSITION OF PRE-SALES ENGINEER - ABUJA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am pleased to be applying for the position of Pre-Sales Engineer at Snapnet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a conscientious person who works hard and pays attention to details. I&rsquo;m flexible, quick to pick up new skills and eager to learn from others. I also have lots of ideas and enthusiasm. I&rsquo;m keen to work for a company with a great reputation and high profile like [Snapnet].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a Field Support Engineer at my current job, I have a wealth of experience working for the past 6yrs exhibiting my skills and competence in carrying out organizational goals effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Highlighted below are few key roles:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Provide remote technical support to field engineers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Incident management; first call resolution to clients&rsquo; complaints.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Prompt response to inbound calls and emails.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Follow up on all unresolved complaint/open ticket closure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Implementing and providing Technical Support in LAN / WAN Networks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; On-site-fault Diagnostic and Resolution of Client&rsquo;s circuit and LAN.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Attending meetings that require technical inputs with the sales team for prospect and existing clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Conducting Site Surveys for Installations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a proven ability to multitask or deliver on multiple tasks within tight timelines, I also am a team player and builder with leadership skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am fully aware of the role and responsibilities that need to be shouldered. I would like to attend the interview if considered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moses A. Omole</p>', 'omolemoses@gmail_SPC_com|07039803012_SPC_08079400280|plot592_SPC_independenceavenue_SPC_fct_SPC_abuja_SPC_nigeria_SPC_profileexperiencedne