(349, 934, 'Ifeanyi Ike', 'ififrank2013@gmail.com', '+2348064569636', 'Flat 3 A35C Brains & Hammers City Estate, Lifecamp, Abuja', NULL, '34', 'male', 'married', 'cv_upload/073829acde2eaae511316b5cbe3aa643.pdf', '<p>Sir/Madam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EXPRESSION OF INTEREST FOR THE POSITION OF DATA SCIENTIST<br />\r\nIt is with great pleasure that I am submitting my application for this advertised position. My long term career goal is to be the best in information management and data driven solutions. I have particular interest in systems that combine multidisciplinary approach with data-driven technologies to provide insights to support decision making. This inspired my passion in data management and data science with special interest in geospatial and non-spatial data analysis. I have a B.Sc degree in Geography from Enugu State University of Science and Technology in Nigeria. To further put this passion in the right direction, I did my masters level degree in M.Sc Remote Sensing and GIS at Ahmadu Bello University, Zaria where I excelled as the best candidate of my set. My research paper has also won different awards and has been published in two peer reviewed journals.<br />\r\nI am a target oriented professional with advanced working knowledge of ArcGIS, QGIS, GRASS, Idrisi GIS software and PostgreSql database, and with very high proficiency in SQL and the use of MS-word, Excel, Access, Power Point, SPSS, Feature Manipulation Engine (SafeFME) in managing big data. I also have advanced knowledge in designing mobile data collection and data visualization tools including Kibana, Tableau, Redash, Google studio and more. In addition to this, I have high proficiency in python programming, data science, machine learning and deep learning in python.<br />\r\nI possess over six (6) years of professional experience in data analysis, and data management with proven track record of diligence, integrity and strong sense of commitment to high standards in what I do. My expertise, operational experience, training and achievements in my previous and current organizations make me well suited on the essential requirements of this current position. During the course of my job experiences, I have joined in designing data management systems. For instance, in my current employment, I worked with a team to design a location intelligent web-based application which supports decision makers in making informed and timely decisions on their field planning and field monitoring activities. This application is being used to support different projects in Nigeria at the moment.<br />\r\nIt would be a great honour for me to join your team of experts as I have been a long time follower of the great work done by your team and I am especially impressed with the prospects of this current position as it is fully in line with my long term career goal. Not only am I eager to contribute to what the team has done, I am also motivated to learn more from the team.<br />\r\nI appreciate you taking the time to look over my application. Kindly let me know if there are further information you may need in consideration for this position. I look forward to being in touch with you.<br />\r\nThanks.</p>', 'ifeanyifranklinike_SPC_databaseadministrator&spatialdataanalystkano_SPC_234_SPC_nigeria·ififrank@2013@gmail_SPC_comprofileapassionatedatabasemanagerandspatialanalystwithover5yearsofexperienceindesigningmobiledatacollectionformsinxls_SPC_managingcomplexgeo-databases tosupportapplicationsandperformingvariousanalyticsofspatialdata_SPC_ialsohaveproventrackrecordindesigningautomatedtoolsforqualityassuranceprotocolsandindesigningtechnicaldocumentstosupportcommunicationandbusinessanalysiscomponentsofapplicationspecifications_SPC_employmenthistorycoordinator_SPC_technicalgis_SPC_ehealthsystemsafricamar2018–jun2019_SPC_kanocreatedqa/qctechnicaldocumentsfordepartmentalgeodatabaseandapplicationmanagementinlinewithcurrentsopsindataqualitymanagement_SPC_createdandmanagedgeodatabasesforplanfeldprodu